\h Ofa Gami
\toc3 OG
\toc2 Ofa Gami
\toc1 Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Ingangaribar Ak…®nafarim
\mt1 Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Ingangaribar Ak…®nafarim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Levitikas
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, a Livaibar ingangaribav gei, kar ik…®zir God ofa gamir ingangarim damuasa m…®seveziba, me Israelian arazir God…®n ziam fer arazim…®n ganamin adarasi. Ak…®nafarir kam, an Akar Gavgaviba ko Arazir ofa gamir gumaziba damuamibav gei. Egha uaghan an aven, akar gumazamiziba men ik…®r…®m…®rim ak…®ramiba, ko God…®n ziam fer arazibar akaba, ko isar ekiabar dughiabar araziba iti, eght…® gumazamiziba deraghv…®ra dagh fogh dar g…®n mangam.
\ip Arazir kabar m…®ngarim kamak…®n: God a bar zue. A bar arazir aghuiba ko vorogh…®ra itir arazibagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a tuavim Israelian akaz…®, me uan ik…®r…®m…®rim derav…®ram an gan, egh God…®n borogh…®n ikiam. God uab…® bar arazir aghuiba ko arazir vorogh…®ra itibagh ami, e uaghan a ko uari akuva, arazir a ifongezibar amuam. Bizir kam, a bizir bar faragha zuim, ak…®nafarir kam a m…®gei.
\ip Israelian gumazamizir igiaba God…®n akabagh fofoghasa, me Ofa Gamir Gumazibar Ingangaribar Ak…®nafarim…®n sapta 16 ko 7…®n gari. Saptan kabar akar aghuir av…®riba, gumazamiziba is…® arazir aghuibara amus…® men sure damuam. Akar kabar mam, Iesus g…®n uaghan an gun m…®gei. Gumazamizir av…®riba sapta 19:18…®n itir Arazibagh fo, ‚ÄúN…® uab…®ra uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, gumazamizir igharazibagh ifongegh.‚Äù
\c 1
\ms1 Ofabar Araziba
\mr (Sapta 1--7)
\p 
\v 1-2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uab…® bativamin Purirpenim…®n ikia, Israelia m…®k…®masa Moses…®n diaz…® a izi, ez…® a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan gumazitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh, ofan tam inigh mang…®s…®, a uan bulmakaun tam, o sipsip…®n tam, o memen tam inigh mang…®.‚Äù
\s1 Ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba
\p 
\v 3 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam iz…® ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damus…®, a uan bulmakaun okoruam…®n tong…®n bulmakaun apurir tam iniam, kar bulmakaun bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®zitam, a inigh mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n navim an deraghs…®, a bulmakaun kam inigh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®.
\v 4 Egh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damus…® uan dafarim is…®, bulmakaun kam…®n dapanim gis…®n anet…®gh, eght…® God…®n navim gumazir kam…®n deraght…®, an ofan kam inigh…®va an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.
\v 5 Egh a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, bulmakaun kam m…®sueght…®, Aron…®n otariba, me ofa gamir gumaziba, me bulmakaun ghuziba is…®, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n itir ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®riar 4plan da kavamang. Egh kamagh…®ra me ghuzir kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damu.
\v 6 Eght…® g…®n gumazir kam, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim…®n bulmakaun kam…®n inim adegh, an tuziba aghorar…®gh.
\v 7-9 Egh as…®zim…®n muriam ko suemning, a deraghv…®ra da ruegh. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim Aron, an ovavir boriba iz…®, daziba ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim…®n dakozim darigh, egh dar aborogh. Egh me dapanim ko ovim ko as…®zir oteviba bar da is…® deraghv…®ra avim daright…®, avim dar isi mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ofan as…®zir kam…®n mughuriam baregh, a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damus…®, a uan as…®zibar okoruam…®n tong…®n sipsip o memen tam inigh, a sipsip…®n apurim o memen apurir bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®zitam inigh iz…®.
\v 11 Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n an ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n danganir not…®n amadaghan iti nagh…®n, as…®zim m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Eght…® Aron…®n otariba, me ofa gamir gumaziba, me iz…® as…®zir ghuziba inigh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamang.
\v 12-13 Eght…® gumazir kam, as…®zim aghorarigh, egh an muriam ko suemning deragh aning ruegh. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazitam daziba ofa gamir dakozim darigh, dar aborogh, egh as…®zim…®n dapanim ko ovim, ko as…®zir naba ofa gamir dakozim…®n avim…®n deraghv…®ra dar ar…®kigh. Egh ofa gamir gumazim, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rir kam is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngam, eght…® avim dar isi mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ofan as…®zir kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh kuarazim…®n ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim damus…®, a kuarazir me kamagh…®n d…®borim, bunbam a inigh ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®.
\v 15 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir bunbam inigh ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, egh an f…®rim ruivight…® an aremegh. Egh a bunbam…®n dapanim asigh, egh ofa gamir dakozim…®n a tuaght…® avim an isi mang…®t…® a bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Egh a bunbam ruivight…® an ghuzim ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®riam gir…®.
\v 16 Egh a bunbam…®n ar…®ziba asigh, an forivtarir dagheba itim is…®, aruem anadi nagh…®n, danganir me ofa gamir dakozim…®n avereniba ar…®zi nagh…®n anet…®gh.
\v 17 Egh g…®n ofa gamir gumazim bunbam…®n av…®zimning…®n suiragh, an namnam ab…®kigh, egh an av…®zimning bar aning asian mark…®. Egh aneteght…®, avim bar an isi mang…®t…® a bar m…®gh…®righ, averenir k…®nim…®n otogh. A kamagh…®n damut…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramim…®n kuarazir kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.‚Äù
\c 2
\s1 Wit tuamin ofaba
\p 
\v 1 Egha God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam wit…®n ov…®zibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damus…®, a wit…®n iniba am…®sevegh dar dagheba inigh faragh plauan aghuim…®n ingarigh, egh a inigh iz…®. Egh a oliv…®n borem ko m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim itir pauran me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim is…® plauan kam gis…®n aning ingegh,
\v 2 egh a inigh Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba bagh mang…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazitam uan dafarim plauan kam darugh, egh a plauan muziaritam, ko m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim itir pauran me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim, aning…®n dafarir iz…®v…®r…®zim inigh ofa gamir dakozim…®n a tuaght…®, avim an isi mang…®t…® a bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham. Plauan muziarir gumazim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamizir kam, bar plauan nam…®n danganim iniam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, wit tuer ofan kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\v 3 Eght…® plauan nam, an ofa gamir gumazibar daghem. Plauan kaba, gumaziba da inigha iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, da bar zuegha God…®n bizibara, eght…® gumazir k…®niba da inian kogham. Ofa gamir gumazibara, da iniam.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúEght…® ia bret, bretba tuer danganim…®n aven a tuagh an nam inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damus…®, ia yis sara veregh an damuan mark…®. Ia plaua inigh oliv…®n borem sara a veregh, egh ia bret…®n damigh an ofa damu. Kamagh…®n, ia bret…®n damuan aghuagh…®va, ia bret…®n baravim damigh, egh oliv…®n borem a daghuigh.
\v 5 Egh ia ofa bagh ain…®n baravim gis…®n plaua tus…®, ia plauan aghuir yis bar puvat…®zim inigh. Egh ia faragh oliv…®n borem sara a veregh, egh a tu.
\v 6 Ia plauan kam bar a nguems…®righ, borem a gingegh Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damu.
\v 7 Egh ia ofa damuamin bret…®n ingar m…®ner ekiam…®n a tuagh, plauan bar aghuir yis puvat…®zim inigh, faragh oliv…®n borem sara a veregh a tuagh.
\v 8 A isigh g…®vaght…®, ia bret…®n kam inigh ofa gamir gumazitam danight…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damus…® a inigh ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®.
\v 9 Egh g…®n ofa gamir gumazim bret…®n akuar muziaritam inight…®, bret…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamizir kam, bar bret…®n nam…®n danganim inigham. Eght…® a ofa gamir dakozim…®n a tuaght…® avim a isi mang…®t…® a bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, wit tuer ofan kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\v 10 Ez…® bret…®n akuar naba, da ofa gamir gumazibar dagheba. Bret…®n kaba, gumaziba da inigha iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, da bar zuegha God…®n bizibara, eght…® gumazir k…®niba da inian kogham. Ofa gamir gumazibara, da iniam.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúIa yis is…®, bret ko plaua dat…®gh a veregh a inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh mangan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, ia yis o hani is…® ofa dat…®gh a tuaght…®, a bar m…®gh…®right…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngan bar mark…®.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄúIa wit…®n akuar faragh azenim…®n m…®seveziba inigh, yis ko hani dar at…®gh Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh mang…®t…®, deragham. Ez…® ofan yis o hani itim, ia ofa gamir dakozim…®n a tuan mark…®, eght…® an mughuriar aghuim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n mangan mark…®.
\v 13 Amangs…®zim, an Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir ia God ko amizim…®n ababanim gami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia amangs…®zim is…® wit tuer ofaba bar dar ar…®kigh. Egh ia amangs…®zim ofan tam dar…®ghs…® ok…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúIa azenim…®n faragha wit…®n ov…®zir m…®sevezir akuaba inigh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damus…®, ia faragh bretba tuer danganim…®n aven da tus…®, da nguems…®righ, egh da inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh mang…®.
\v 15 Ez…® wit tuer ofan kam, ia oliv…®n borem ko, m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim itir pauran, me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim is…® wit…®n nguems…®r…®zir kam gis…®n aning ingegh.
\v 16 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, wit…®n kam…®n muziaritam ko, oliv…®n borem ko m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim itir pauran me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim, bar ada inigh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n avim…®n da tueght…® dar mughuriam otivam. Wit…®n nguems…®r…®zir muziarir gumazim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamizir kam, bar wit…®n nam…®n danganim iniam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, wit tuer ofan kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.‚Äù
\c 3
\s1 God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofaba
\p 
\v 1 Egha God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa damus…®, a bulmakaun ofa damus…® ifongegh, kamagh…®n a bulmakaun apurim o bulmakaun amebar bar aghuir, duatam an m…®karzim gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®zir tam inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n iz…®.
\v 2 Gumazir kam uan bulmakau inigh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®, egh uan dafarim is…® faragh bulmakaun dapanim dat…®gh, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Eght…® Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba, me bulmakaun kam…®n ghuziba inigh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamang.
\v 3 Eght…® gumazir kam God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofa bagh, bulmakaun akuar taba inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God danight…®, ofa gamir gumaziba ofan m…®n avim…®n da tuegh. Bulmakaun akuar kaba dar kara. An navim ko muriaba avarazir oviba bar ada inigh.
\v 4 Egh an og…®agharim…®n itir ov…®zimning, ko aning…®n ovim sara, ko beram…®n akuar aghuim inigh.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúEght…® Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba, bizir kaba ko ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba inigh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tueght…®, avim bar dar isi mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ofan as…®zir kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa damus…®, a uan sipsip ko memebar okoruabar tong…®n as…®zir apurim o as…®zir amebam inigh, kar sipsip o memen bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zim.
\v 7 Egh gumazir kam sipsip…®n tam…®n ofa damus…®, kamagh…®n ana inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n iz…®.
\v 8 Egh a uan dafarim is…® sipsip…®n kam…®n dapanim gis…®n dat…®gh, egh a God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra sipsip m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Eght…® ofa gamir gumaziba as…®zir kam…®n ghuziba is…®, ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamang.
\v 9 Eght…® gumazir kam, God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofa bagh, sipsip…®n as…®zir akuar taba inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngt…®, ofa gamir gumaziba ofan m…®n da tuam. Sipsip…®n ovir kaba bar, kar an navim ko muriam avarazir oviba, ko an puer m…®ngarir ak…®ragharim…®n borogh…®ra itir ovir bar ekiam itiba inigh. Egh an oviba itir puer m…®ngarir ak…®ragharim…®n borogh…®ra itim atugh, an ovir kaba bar da inigh.
\v 10 Egh an og…®agharim…®n itir ov…®zimning, ko aning…®n ovim sara, ko beram…®n akuar aghuim inigh.
\v 11 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim bizir kaba is…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh daghem…®n ofan m…®n, ofa gamir dakozim gis…®n avim…®n da tu mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam memen ofa damus…®, an a inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n mang…®.
\v 13 Egh a uan dafarim is…® memen dapanim gis…®n dat…®gh, egh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Eght…® Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba an ghuziba is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamang.
\v 14 Eght…® gumazir kam memen ovir m…®saziaba inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngt…®, ofa gamir gumaziba ofan m…®n da tuam. An an navim ko muriam avarazir oviba bar da inigh.
\v 15 Egh an ov…®zir pumuning, ko aning…®n ovim sara inigh, memen beram…®n akuar aghuim inigh.
\v 16 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim bizir kaba is…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh daghem…®n ofan m…®n, ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tueght…®, avim dar isi mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Eght…® oviba bar, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizibara.
\v 17 Ia Israelia, ian tav as…®zir ovim, o ghuzir tabar aman mark…®. Bar markiam. Ia ko ian ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba arazir kam…®n g…®nt…®gh mamagh…®ra ik…®. Egh ia mang…® managh ik…®, ia arazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®v…®ra ik…®.‚Äù
\c 4
\s1 Arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba
\p 
\v 1-2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam deragha fozir puvat…®gha, arazir kuram gamua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavir e m…®kemezir tam abigh…®va, kamagh…®n, a ofan kabar amu.‚Äù
\s1 Ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa
\p 
\v 3 Egha Moses ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúOfa gamir gumazibar dapanim arazir kuram damight…®, an arazir kurar kam gumazamizibar amut…®, me bar os…®mt…®zim ikiam. Kamagh…®n, a bulmakaun apurir bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zir tam inigh. Egh uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damigh.
\v 4 A bulmakaun kam inigh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n itiar akam…®n mang…®gh, dafarim an dapanim gis…®n dat…®gh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 5 Egh ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim bulmakaun ghuzitam inigh, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven mang…®.
\v 6 Egh nir ekiar Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim modozim…®n borogh…®n mang…®, uan dafar puzir tam is…® ghuzim darugh, egh ghuzir muziarim is…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, inir ekiam…®n a gas…®vamang. A 7plan dughiabar kamagh…®n damu.
\v 7 Egh a pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozim iti nagh…®n mang…®, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tugh…®v ik…®. Egh a ghuzitaba is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir biziba bar dar aghuigh. Egh a bulmakaun ghuzir nar ikiav…®ra itir kaba, inigh as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozir azenan itim…®n mang…®, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n tugh…®v ik…®. Egh da is…® ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n m…®ngarim gingegh.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEgh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan kam bagh, a bulmakaun kam…®n navim ko muriaba avarazir oviba bar ada inigh,
\v 9 egh an ov…®zir pumuning ko, aning…®n ovim sara inigh, egh an beram…®n akuar aghuim inigh.
\v 10 Egh ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, ovir m…®saziar kaba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tueght…® da bar isigh m…®gh…®righam, eght…® averenir k…®nimra ikiam. An ofan arazir kam mati, me God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa, me bulmakaun oviba inigha ofa gami.
\v 11-12 Egh a bulmakaun apurir kam…®n as…®zir naba inigh, an inim ko tuziba ko dapanim, suemning ko dafarimning, muriam ko buariba, bar ada inigh, nguibar me itim…®n azenan mang…®va, me avim…®n avereniba inger danganim…®n, God…®n damazim…®n zuezir danganim…®n mang…®. Egh averenir pozim gis…®n daziba arigh avim daborogh as…®zir nar kaba tueght…® da bar isight…® averenir k…®nim otogham.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba
\p 
\v 13 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúIsraelian gumazamiziba deraghv…®ra foghan kogh…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavir me m…®kemezir mam abigh, kamagh…®n me arazir kuram gami. Me fozir puvat…®, me arazir kuram gami, egha guizbang…®ra me uan arazir kam…®n me os…®mt…®zim iti.
\v 14 Me g…®n uan arazir kuram g…®fogh, egh a g…®n amang…®s…®, me uan as…®zibar tong…®n bulmakaun igiar apurir tam inigh an ofa damu. Me arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan kam inigh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n iz…®.
\v 15 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n Israelian gumazir dapaniba uan dafariba is…®, bulmakaun apurir kam…®n dapanim dat…®gh, egh me a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 16 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim bulmakaun apurir kam…®n ghuzitaba inigh, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven mang…®.
\v 17 Egh nir ekiar Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim modozim…®n borogh…®n mang…®, uan dafar puzir tam is…® ghuzim darugh, egh ghuzir muziarim is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, inir ekiam gas…®vamang. A 7plan dughiabar kamagh…®n damu.
\v 18 Egh a pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozir Purirpenim…®n aven iti nagh…®n mang…®, egh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tugh…®v ik…®. Egh a ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n ghuzitaba is…®, bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir biziba bar dar aghuigh. Egh bulmakaun ghuzir nar ikiav…®ra itir kaba, a da inigh as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n tugh…®v ik…®. Egh da is…® ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n m…®ngarim gingegh.
\v 19 Egh g…®n a bulmakaun oviba bar da inigh as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tueght…® da bar isigh m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nimra ikiam.
\v 20 Ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, uab…® uan arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa gami mogh…®n, a kamagh…®ra bulmakaun kam damigh. Ez…® kamagh…®ra ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damut…®, God men arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.
\v 21 Eght…® a g…®n bulmakaun as…®zir naba bar ada inigh, nguibar me itim…®n azenan mang…®gh avim…®n bar ada tuegh, mati a uab…® uan arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa bulmakaun ofa gami. Bulmakaun kam, gumazamiziba bar men arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazir dapanibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba
\p 
\v 22 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazir dapanitam deraghv…®ra foghan kogh…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavir e m…®kemezir tam abigh, kamagh…®n an arazir kuram gami. A fozir puvat…®, an arazir kuram gami, egha guizbang…®ra a uan arazir kam…®n an os…®mt…®zim iti.
\v 23 A g…®n uan arazir kurar kam g…®fogh, egh a g…®n amang…®s…®, memen apurir aghuitam inigh, duatam an m…®karzim…®n ikian mark…®, egh ana inigh ofa bagh iz…®.
\v 24 Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a dafarim is…® memen dapanim gis…®n dat…®gh, egh danganir me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar as…®zibav sozimra tugh, memen kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Memen kam, an arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.
\v 25 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan kam bagh, uan dafarir puzir tam is…® memen ghuzim darugh, egh ghuzir muziaritam is…® as…®ziba da bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir biziba bar dar aghuigh. Egh ghuzir naba is…® as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®ngarim gingegh.
\v 26 Egh a memen oviba ofa gamir dakozim…®n, da tueght…® da bar isigh m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Ofa gamir gumazim arazir kamra damu, mati me God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabar m…®n me meme m…®sogha an oviba isa ofa gami. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir dapanir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damu, eght…® God an arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazir k…®nibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27-31 \xt D…®boboniba 15:27-28\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazir k…®nitam o amizir k…®nitam deraghv…®ra foghan kogh…®va, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavir e m…®kemezir tam abigh, kamagh…®n an arazir kuram gamiz…®, arazir kurar kam…®n os…®mt…®zim an iti.
\v 28 Egh a g…®n bizir kam g…®fogh, egh uan arazir kuram g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damuam. A memen amebar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zimra inigh, egh uan arazir kurar an amizim bagh ofa damus…® a inigh iz…®.
\v 29 Egh a uan dafarim is…® memen dapanim gis…®n dat…®gh, danganir me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar as…®zibav sozi nagh…®ra tugh, a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Memen kam, an arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.
\v 30 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim uan dafarir puzir tam is…® memen ghuzim darugh, egh ghuzir muziarir taba is…® as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir biziba bar dar aghuigh. Egh a ghuzir nar ikiav…®ra itim inigh, as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®ngarim gingegh.
\v 31 Egh a memen oviba bar da inigh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuegh. Ofa gamir gumazim arazir kamra damu, mati me God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabar m…®n me meme m…®sogha an oviba isa ofa gami. Egh oviba ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tu mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ofan kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam. Kamagh…®ra, ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir k…®nir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damut…®, God an arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.
\p 
\v 32 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® sipsip…®n ofa damus…®, a sipsip…®n amebar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zimra inigh iz…®.
\v 33 Egh a uan dafarim is…® sipsip…®n dapanim gis…®n dat…®gh, danganir me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar as…®zibav sozi nagh…®n tugh, a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Sipsip…®n kam, an arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.
\v 34 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, uan dafarir puzir tam is…® sipsip…®n ghuzim darugh, egh ghuzir muziarir taba is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir biziba bar dar aghuigh. Egh a ghuzir nar ikiav…®ra itim inigh, egh as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®ngarim gingegh.
\v 35 Egh a sipsip…®n oviba bar da inigh ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuegh. Ofa gamir gumazim arazir kamra, mati arazir me God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabagh amibar m…®n, a sipsip…®n kam…®n oviba inigh ofa damu. An an oviba tueght…® da bar isigh m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham. Kamagh…®ra, ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir k…®nir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damu, eght…® God an arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.‚Äù
\c 5
\s1 Arazir kurar igharagha garir maba g…®n amadir ofaba
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazitam gumazir igharazim…®n garima, a bizim gami, o a gumazir igharazim barazima, a bizim m…®keme, ez…® g…®n jas, kot…®n aven bizir kam…®n gun m…®k…®masa an diagha an azangs…®si. Ez…® gumazir kam kot…®n aven bizir a fozir kam…®n gun m…®kemezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n an arazir kuram God…®n damazim…®n a gamigha os…®mt…®zim iti.
\p 
\v 2 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam deragh n…®ghnighan kogh, God m…®kemezir bizir m…®zezir tam…®n porogham, gumazir kam a God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. A mati as…®zir atiar aremezir kuam, o nguibam…®n as…®zir kuar God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezim, o as…®zir davaragha aruir God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezim. As…®zir kam ti aremez…®, an kuam pura nguazim gir…®ghav iti. Ez…® gumazir kam deragha ganizir puvat…®gha iza, as…®zim…®n porogha God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze. Egh g…®n a uan arazir kurar an amizibagh foght…®, arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 3 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam deragh n…®ghnighan kogh, egh God…®n damazim…®n bizir m…®zezir gumazim o amizim…®n m…®karzim…®n itim…®n porogh, gumazir kam God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham. Egh g…®n a uan arazir kurar an amizibagh fogham, eght…® arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Mak 6:23; Aposel 23:12\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam deragh n…®ghnighan kogh, bizitam damus…® guizbang…®ra pura p…®n akakagh m…®k…®mam, a kamagh…®n God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Egh g…®n a uan arazir kurar an amizim g…®foght…®, an arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúGumazitam arazir kurar kamagh…®n garitam gami, an os…®mt…®zim inigha g…®fa, egh a uan os…®mt…®zim…®n gun m…®kemegh.
\v 6 Egh a uan arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim ag…®vs…® sipsip…®n amebatam o memen amebatam is…® ofan m…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh a inigh iz…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam…®n arazir kuram g…®n amang…®s…®, as…®zir kam…®n ofa damut…®, God an arazir kuram g…®n amadagham.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúArazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim itir gumazim, onganarazim damu sipsip ko meme givezamin dag…®aba otevegh, a kuarazir bunbar pumuning inigh uan os…®mt…®zim ag…®vs…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh iz…®. Eght…® bunbar tam, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan otogham, eght…® bunbar igharazim, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim…®n otogham.
\v 8 Gumazir kam aning inigh ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®t…®, a kuarazir bunbar tam inigh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu. Ofa gamir gumazim bunbam…®n f…®rim ruivight…® an aremeght…®, an an dapanim asian mark…®.
\v 9 Egh a ghuzir muziarim inigh ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®riam…®n a kavamang, bunbam…®n f…®rim ruivight…® an ghuzir naba bar ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®ngarim giram. Kuarazir bunbar kam, an arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.
\v 10 Egh g…®n a bunbar igharazim…®n, bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa damu. A ofan kam…®n arazim…®n g…®n mang…®. Egh kamagh…®ra ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® a bagh ofa damu, eght…® God an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúGumazir os…®mt…®zim itim, bar dag…®abagh asagh…®va kuarazimning givezan iburagh, a 1 kilogrem plauan aghuitam inigh iz…®. Egh, a wit…®n ov…®zim tuer ofan m…®n amiz…® mogh…®n, an oliv…®n borem ko, m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim itir pauran me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim is…® a gingan mark…®. Puvat…®, plauan kam, kar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.
\v 12 Egh a ofa inigh ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®, eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, uan dafarim is…® plauan kam darugh, plauan dafarir iz…®v…®r…®zim inigh ofan igharaziba sara ofa gamir dakozim…®n a tuaght…®, avim an isi mang…®t…® a bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham. Plauan muziarir kam, gumazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamizir kam, plauan nam bar an danganim ini. Kar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa.
\v 13 Tuavir kamra ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam…®n arazir kuram bagh ofa damight…®, God an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham. Eght…® ikiav…®ra itir plauan naba, ofa gamir gumaziba da inigh dar amam, mati wit…®n ov…®zir nar me ofa bagha tueba.‚Äù
\s1 Os…®mt…®ziba agevir ofaba
\p 
\v 14 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme,
\v 15 ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam deragha fozir puvat…®gha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngamin biziba bak…®n…®ghnigh, egha an arazir kuram gami. Egh gumazir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damu, bizir kam ikarvagh uan os…®mt…®zim ag…®vagham. Ofa gamir gumazim a m…®kemeght…®, a uan as…®zibar okoruabar tong…®n sipsip…®n apurir bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zitam inigh iz…®. Ofa gamir gumazim, sipsip…®n gumazim inigha izezir kam…®n ivezim…®n d…®bobonim at…®gham. Kar os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa.
\v 16 Eght…® dag…®ar a isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ngizir puvat…®zir kaba, a dat…®r…®gh…®n a dan…®ng, egh ua dag…®ataba is…® dagh is…®n dat…®gh. A pura 5plan biziba ini, kamagh…®n a 6plan biziba, bizir kaba ikaragham. Egh da is…® ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngigh. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, sipsip…®n kam inigh, gumazir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim ag…®vamin ofa damu, eght…® God an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.
\p 
\v 17 ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam deragh n…®ghnighan kogh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavitam abigham, kamagh…®n an arazir kuram gamigha God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zim iti, egh ivezir kuram iniam.
\v 18 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan as…®zibar okoruabar tong…®n sipsip…®n apurir bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zitam inigh, ofan m…®n ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®, egh uan arazir kurabar os…®mt…®ziba ak…®r da ag…®fagh. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim sipsip…®n gumazim inigha izezir kam…®n ivezim d…®borogh a dat…®gh. Eght…® gumazim sipsip…®n kamagh garitam, ofa gamir gumazim bagh a inigh iz…®t…®, a gumazir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa damight…®, God an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.
\v 19 Sipsip…®n kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, an os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa.‚Äù
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1-7 \xt D…®boboniba 5:5-8\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme,
\v 2 ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam uan namakam…®n bizim puram a inigha, uam a ikarvaghasa akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamigha, g…®n bizir kam uam a dan…®ngan aghua, kamagh…®n a deraghav…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®, egha an arazir kuram gami. A namakam…®n bizim okeme, o namakam gifaragha an bizibagh etui,
\v 3 o a bizitam…®n garima, gumazir igharazim an ovenge, ez…® a ifara ghaze, bar guizbang…®ra, k…® an ganizir puvat…®, kamagh…®n, an arazir kuram gami.
\v 4-5 Gumazir arazir kabagh amim, a God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zim inigha g…®fa. Egh g…®n a uan os…®mt…®zim g…®fogh, egh an oker arazim ko ifavarir arazim…®n inizir bizir kaba, a ua da ikaragh. A uan os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vs…® ofa damuamin dughiam…®n, a bizir kaba ikarvagh da is…® dar ghuavim dan…®ngigh. A faragha 5plan biziba ini, egh a 6plan biziba uam a da ikaragh.
\v 6 A sipsip…®n apuritam inigh ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®, uan arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim agevir ofan m…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damu. Ofa gamir gumazim a m…®kemeght…®, a uan as…®zibar tong…®n sipsip…®n apurir bar aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zitam, inigh iz…®. Ofa gamir gumazim sipsip…®n gumazim inigha izezir kam…®n ivezim…®n d…®bobonim at…®gham.
\v 7 Egh ofa gamir gumazim, a gumazir arazir kuram gamizibagh amizim…®n os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vs…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ofa damut…®, God an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.‚Äù
\s1 Ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar araziba
\p 
\v 8 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme:
\v 9 ‚ÄúN…® ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar arazibar gun Aron ko an otaribav m…®kemegh. Me ofan kam ofa gamir dakozim…®n a tuagh, egh aneteght…®, avim an isi d…®mangan ik…® mang…®t…® am…®nim tiragh. D…®mangan avim isi mamagh…®ra ik…®, egh mungeghan mark…®.
\v 10 Eght…® g…®n, ofa gamir gumazim, korotiar ruarir me inir aghuim…®n ingarizim arugh, egh g…®n trausiziar otevir me nir aghuim…®n ingarizim is…® aven anerugh, egh g…®n an ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramim…®n averenim inigh, averenir kam ofan ovim an iti. Egh ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n nguazim…®n a ingegh.
\v 11 Egh a g…®n uan korotiam suegh korotiar igharazibar aghuigh, averenir kam inigh men d…®peniba itir danganim…®n azenan mang…®, nan damazim…®n danganir zuezim…®n anet…®gh.
\v 12 Eght…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n avim isi mamagh…®ra ik…®, egh mungan mark…®. Egh m…®zarazibar zurara, ofa gamir gumazim dazibar avim dar…®gh mamagh…®ra ik…®. Egh an as…®zir bar isia m…®gh…®riba inigh, da is…® avim…®n deragh dar arigh da tueght…®, da bar isigh m…®gh…®right…® averenir k…®nim otogham. Egh a God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan oviba inigh, avir kam…®n da tueght…® da bar isigh m…®gh…®right…® averenir k…®nim otogham.
\v 13 Avim zurara ofa gamir dakozim…®n isi mamagh…®ra ik…®. Ia avim ateght…® a mungeghan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Wit tuamin ofabar arazim
\p 
\v 14 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúWit tuamin ofabar arazim kamak…®n. Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumazitam ofan wit tuamin kam is…® nan damazim…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n mang…®, nan akagh na dan…®ngam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.
\v 15 Egh ofan kam bagh, ofa gamir gumazim uan dafarim is…® plauan kam darugh, egh dafarir z…®v…®rizim…®n an plaua inigh, an itir borer muziaritam, ko m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuir pauran me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim bar a inigh. Egh a bizir kaba bar, da is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tueght…®, avim dar isi mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham. Plauan muziarir gumazim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamizir kam, bar plauan nam…®n danganim inigham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, wit…®n ofa tuamin kam…®n mughuriam baregh…®va, a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\v 16 Eght…® ofa gamir gumaziba plauan nar ikiav…®ra itibar am…®. Me plaua inigh yis puvat…®zir bret…®n ingarigh, egh God bativamin Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven anem…®.
\v 17 Kar ofan dagher nar me iniamba. Plauan kam, k…® ofa gamir gumaziba bagha anem…®sefe. Plauan kam, a bar nan bizimra, mati arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba ko gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba agevir ofaba, da nan biziba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me yis sara bret…®n kam veregh a tuan mark…®. Me puram a tuam.
\v 18 Aron…®n ovavir boribar tong…®n gumazibara, me vaghvagh bret…®n kam amam. Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rir dagher kaba, merara, da iniam. Egh g…®n izamin dughiabar zurara, Aron…®n ovavir boriba, ofan nar kaba ini mamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® gumazitam, o bizitam ofan nar kabar porogh…®va, a nan bizimram otogh egh bar anogoregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 20 ‚ÄúAron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba, me igiamra ofa gamir ingangarim isir dughiam…®n ofan tam damigh. Egh me ofa gamir dughiam…®n gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a na bagh ofabar amu. A plauan tam inight…®, an os…®mt…®zim 1 kilogrem…®n tugh, a mati me dughiabar zurara wit tuer ofan ababanimra inigh. A plauan kam…®n akuatam is…® m…®zarazim…®n ofa damigh, egh aruem mag…®r…®t…®, an akuar nam…®n ofa damu.
\v 21 An oliv…®n borem sara bar deragh plauan kam ko a veregh, egh ofa bagh amir ain…®n baravim gis…®n plaua tuagh. Egh g…®n aneb…®gh…®rarigh na dan…®ng, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. Eght…® k…® ofan kam…®n mughuriam baregh, a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\v 22 Eght…® g…®n izamin dughiam…®n, me Aron…®n ovavir boribar gumazibar tong…®n, ofa gamir gumazim am…®seveght…®, an Aron…®n danganim inigh ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n otogh, egh a Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofan kamagh…®ra garim damuam. Ofan kam, a nan bizimra, kamagh…®n, a ofa ateght…® a bar isi m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogh.
\v 23 Ofa gamir gumaziba wit…®n ofan kam…®n muziarir tabar aman mark…®. Puvat…®. Me aneteght…® a bar is…® m…®gh…®righ.‚Äù
\s1 Arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba
\p 
\v 24 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\v 25 ‚ÄúN…® ofan arazir kuraba g…®n amadir arazibar gun Aron ko an otaribav kemegh. Arazir kam a kamak…®n. Me arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…®, nan damazim…®n as…®zim m…®suegh ofa damu. Me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar, as…®ziba m…®sozir danganim…®n as…®zim m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Ka bar nan ofa.
\v 26 Ofa gamir gumazim, as…®zir kam is…® arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu, egh a uab…® God bativamin Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven as…®zir tuzir kam amam, kar danganir na baghav…®ra itim.
\v 27 Eght…® gumazitam, ofan kam…®n as…®zir tuzim…®n porogh, egh a nan bizimram otogh…®va, bar anogoregham. Eght…® as…®zim…®n ghuzim inim o bizitam gireght…®, ia nan Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven a ruegh.
\v 28 Ofa gamir gumazim, ofan kam nguazir m…®nem…®n anevigh, a g…®n m…®ner kam ab…®kigh. A bras…®n m…®nem…®n anevigh…®va, d…®pam…®n deragh a ruva a isegh.
\v 29 Ofan kamagh…®n garim, a nan bizimra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazibar adarazir gumazitam ifongegh, a ofan kam…®n as…®zir tuzim am…®.
\v 30 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, ofan kam…®n ghuzitaba inigh, na bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven mang…®gh, arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin ingangarim damut…® ofa gamir gumaziba ofan as…®zir tuzir kam aman mark…®. Me as…®zir tuziba avim…®n bar da tu mang…®t…® da m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham.‚Äù
\c 7
\s1 Os…®mt…®ziba agevir ofaba
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme: ‚ÄúOs…®mt…®ziba agevir ofan kaba, da bar God…®n bizibara. Ofan kabar Araziba kamak…®n.
\v 2 Me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba bagha as…®zibav sozir danganim…®n, me os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa bagh sipsip m…®sueght…®, an aremegh. Eght…® me sipsip…®n kam…®n ghuziba is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamang.
\v 3 Gumazir ofan kam damuamim, a sipsip…®n oviba, ko an puer m…®ngarim…®n borogh…®ra itir ovir bar ekiam itiba, ko a navim ko muriam avarazir oviba inigh.
\v 4 Egh an ov…®zimning ko oviba sara inigh, egh uaghan sipsip…®n beram…®n akuar aghuim inigh.
\v 5 Egh ofa gamir gumazim, ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tueght…®, avim dar isi mang…®t…® da bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim otogham, mati me ofa isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®di mogh…®n damu. Kar ofan os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa.
\v 6 Ofa gamir gumazibar adarazir gumazitam, as…®zir tuzir kam am…®s…® ifuegh anem…®. Kar God…®n ofa, an ofa gamir gumaziba bagha a ginaba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me God…®n Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven anem…®, kar God…®n danganimra.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúArazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa, ko os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa, aning ofan arazir vam…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazim, ofan kamagh garir kamning damuva, a uab…®, ua bagh ofan kam…®n as…®zir tuzim iniam.
\v 8 Ofa gamir gumazim bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa damuva, a ua bagh as…®zim…®n inim iniam.
\v 9 Egha kamagh…®ra, ofa gamir gumazim, wit…®n ofan me bretba tuer danganim…®n tueziba, ko wit…®n ofan me nguazir m…®nem…®n tueziba, ko wit…®n ofan me ain…®n baravim…®n tueziba bar, a ua bagh da inigh dar am…®.
\v 10 Wit…®n ofan igharazir me tuezir puvat…®ziba, maba me oliv…®n borem…®n sara da vere, maba me plauan ofan k…®nibagh ami, da bar Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumazibar biziba. Me da tuiragh d…®bobonir vam…®ran g…®n mang…® vaghvagh Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ng.‚Äù
\s1 God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba
\p 
\v 11 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan arazim kamak…®n.
\v 12 Gumazitam God m…®nab…® a ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofan kam damus…® ifongegh, an as…®zir ofan God m…®nabim inigh, egh uaghan yis puvat…®zir bret…®n taba sara ofa damu. Bret…®n kabar kara: plauan me oliv…®n borem sara veregha ingarizir bretba, ko me oliv…®n borem…®n aghuizir bisketba, ko oliv…®n borer ekiam avarazir bretba, da inigh ofa damu.
\v 13 Egh a uaghan bret…®n rubuzir yis itir taba inigh, egh God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan kam sara damuva a m…®nab…®.
\v 14 A bret…®n kaba vaghvagh dar akuatam inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngigh. Bret…®n kaba, ofa gamir gumazim…®n dagheba. Ofa gamir gumazir kam, a God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan as…®zim…®n ghuziba inigh, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®riabar da kavamang.
\v 15 Eght…® gumazir God m…®nab…®va a ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa gamim, ofa gamir dughiar kamra, an as…®zir tuzir naba bar dar amegh. An as…®zir tuziba ateght…®, da ik…® mang…® dughiar igharazim…®n otivan mark…®.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam, uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir God koma amizim ak…®ramin ofa damus…®, o a uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…® ofa damu, o God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa damu, egh gumazir kam ofa gamir dughiam…®n, an as…®zir kam…®n tuzir tabar am…®, egh am…®mzaraghan uaghan tuzir nabar ameght…®, kamagh…®n deragham.
\v 17 Egh me dughiar namba 2…®n, da g…®vaghan koght…®, as…®zir tuzir naba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, me dughiar namba 3…®n avim…®n bar da tueght…®, da bar mogh…®ra isi m…®gh…®righ.
\v 18 Me dughiar namba 3…®n as…®zir tuzir katam ameght…®, God gumazir kam…®n ofan kam inighan kogham. Ofan kam, a God…®n damazim…®n deraghan kogh, egh pura mang…®gh gumazir kam…®n akurvaghan kogham. Eght…® God suam, n…®n ofan kam bar m…®zegha kuriz…® k…® bar an aghua. Eght…® gumazir manam as…®zir tuzir kam am…®va, an os…®mt…®zim ikiam.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúEght…® God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan as…®zir tuzim, bizir m…®z…®r…®zitam…®n porogham, a God…®n damazim…®n zueghan kogham. Eght…® me as…®zir tuzir kam aman mark…®. Me as…®zir tuzir kam avim…®n a tuaght…® a bar isi m…®gh…®righ.
\p ‚ÄúGumazamizir God…®n damazim…®n zueziba, merara God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan as…®zir tuzim am…®.
\v 20 Eght…® ian tav God…®n damazim…®n zueghan kogh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofan as…®zir tuzim ameght…®, me a batueght…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n aven ikian kogham.
\v 21 Eght…® ian tav uaghan, bizir God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir tam…®n suiragham, ka ti as…®zir zuezir puvat…®zitam, o bizir m…®zegha gumazamizibar m…®karzibar itiba, o as…®zir m…®z…®r…®zir k…® aghuaziba, dar suiragh, egh gumazir kam g…®n ofan as…®zir tuzir kam ameght…®, me a batueght…® a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Israelia as…®zir oviba ko ghuzibar aman kogham
\p 
\v 22-23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa bulmakaun oviba ko sipsip…®n oviba, ko memen oviba, dar aman mark…®.
\v 24 Ia bulmakaun uab…® aremezim o as…®zir atiam m…®soghez…® aremezim, ia an ovim aman mark…®. Egh ia ingangarir igharazitam damus…® an ovim inight…® deragham.
\v 25 Eght…® gumazitam, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamizir as…®zim…®n ovitam ameght…®, me a batueght…®, a ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n aven ikian kogham.
\v 26 \x - \xo 7:26-27 \xt Jenesis 9:4; Ofa Gami 17:10-14; 19:26; God…®n Araziba 12:16; 12:23; 15:23\x*Ia Israelia, ia managh iti, ia ghuziba sara as…®ziba ko, ghuziba sara kuarazibar aman mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\v 27 Gumazitam o amizitam, Akar Gavgavir ghuzibar aman koghamin kam abight…®, me a batueght…®, a ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n aven ikian kogham.‚Äù
\s1 Ofan as…®zir tuzir naba, me ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngam
\p 
\v 28-29 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan tong…®n itir gumazitam, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa damus…® as…®zim inigh iz…®, an as…®zir otevitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghv…®ra anem…®sefegh.
\v 30 Gumazir kam uab…® as…®zir otevir kam inigh iz…®, avim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damu. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n as…®zir otevir kaba kamak…®n, as…®zir ovim ko an amagapam…®n itir tuzim. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damu. A uan dafarimning…®n amagapam…®n itir as…®zir tuzim…®n suiragh a fegh a damut…® a God…®n damazim…®n ighuavamang.
\v 31 Ofa gamir gumazim ofa gamir dakozim…®n ovim tuaght…®, avim an isi mang…®t…® a bar m…®gh…®righ, averenir k…®nim otogham. Eght…® Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumaziba uari dam…®s…®, an amagapam…®n itir tuzim inigh.
\v 32 Eght…® as…®zir kam…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir buaragharim, gumazim a is…® ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngigh. As…®zir kam, a God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa.
\v 33 Kamagh…®n Aron…®n adarazir tong…®n ofa gamir gumazim, a ghuzim ko ovim…®n ofa gami, ez…® as…®zir buaragharim, kar an bizim.
\v 34 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n fegha ighuavamadir amagapar tuzim, ko as…®zir kam…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir buaragharim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian gumazamizibar ofabar tong…®n aning inigha, ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®ngi, kar Aron ko an ovavir boriba. Egh g…®n otivamin dughiabar zurara, ofa gamir gumaziba ofan otevir kaba iniam.
\v 35 Gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh avim…®n ofan amibar tong…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, as…®zir tuzir otevir kamning, ginabagha ghaze, Aron ko an ovavir boriba, dughiar a me gamiz…®, me an ofa gamir gumazibar otozim…®n ikegh, zurara mang…®, me as…®zir tuzir otevir kamning iniam.
\v 36 Dughiar kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, me ofan as…®zir tuzir otevir kamning is…® ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ng. Egh me arazir kam zurara an g…®n mang…®v…®ra ik…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 37 Akar Gavgavir kaba bar, kar ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko, wit tuer ofaba ko, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba ko, os…®mt…®ziba agevir ofaba ko, gumaziba m…®sevima me ofa gamir gumazibar otivir ofaba ko, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba.
\v 38 Israelia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Akar Gavgavir kaba Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n da isa Moses gan…®ngi. Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Akar Gavgaviba Israelia gan…®ga ghaze, me uan ofaba inigh a bagh izam.
\c 8
\ms1 Aron uan otariba ko, // ofa gamir ingangariba
\mr (Sapta 8--10)
\s1 God gumaziba m…®s…®vt…® me ofa gamir gumazibar otivamin ofa
\r (Ua Me Ini 29:1-37)
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 2-3 ‚ÄúN…® Aron ko an otariba sara inigh na bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®. Egh ofa gamir gumazim…®n korotiaba ko ingangarir kam bagh me am…®s…®vamin oliv…®n borem inigh. Egh arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® bulmakaun apurir tam ko sipsip…®n apurimning ko yis puvat…®zir bret…®n ak…®rar iz…®vazir tam, bizir kaba sara inigh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n mang…®. Egh gumazamiziba bar men diaght…®, me Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n iz…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavim baregha an g…®n zui. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar iza God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n uari akufa.
\v 5 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n damuamin kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a damuasa na m…®keme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Egha Moses Aron ko an otariba inigha iza gumazamizibar damazim…®n tugha, me gamiz…® me d…®pam…®n uari rue.
\v 7 A faraghav…®ra ofa gamir gumazim…®n korotiar ruarir aven azuim isa Aron garugha, inir ruarir ivariam gitim isa an ivariam gike. Egha Moses korotiar ruarir azenan itim a garu. Egha a korotiar otevir azenan azuim a garugha anem…®gh…®nasa inir sazir kurkazir aghuiba itim isa an ivariam gike.
\v 8 Egha forivtarir inim isa Aron…®n evarim gike, egha God…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghamin dag…®amning isa forivtarir inir an evarim…®n itim garu.
\v 9 Egha inir dapanir asuar ruarim Aron…®n dapanim gighui. Egha gol medel isa an inir dapanir asuar ruarim gitoro. Medal…®n kam, kamagh…®n men aka, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazimra. Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Moses arazir kaba bar dagh ami.
\p 
\v 10 Egha Moses, oliv…®n borer God baghv…®ra ikiamin bizibagh inger kam, inigha ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim ginga, bizir an aven itiba sara bar dagh inge. Egha arazir kam…®n a bizir kaba am…®sevez…®, da bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizibara.
\v 11 Egha a oliv…®n borer nam inigha ghua, 7plan dughiabar ofa gamir dakozim ko ofa gamir dakozim…®n biziba, ko soroghafariba ruer itarir ekiam ko anefamin dakozim, a bar borem…®n da kavamangi. Egha arazir kam…®n Moses bizir kaba am…®sevez…®, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizibar otifi.
\v 12 Egha Moses borer muziarim isa Aron…®n dapanim ginge, ez…® arazir kam…®n an Aron am…®sevez…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n oto.
\v 13 Egha Moses, Aron…®n otariba inigha iza ofa gamir gumazibar korotiar ruarir aven azuiba isa me gaghua, inir ruarir ivariam gitim isa men ivariabagh ikegha, men dapanir asuabar inir ruariba isa men dapanibagh ighuigha da ifefe. Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Moses arazir kaba bar dagh ami.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® bizir kam g…®vaz…®, Moses arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damuamin bulmakaun apurim…®n akua izez…®, Aron uan otariba ko uan dafariba isa bulmakaun dapanim gis…®n da ar…®ki.
\v 15 Moses bulmakaun kam m…®suegha, an ghuzir maba ini. Egha uan dafarir puzim isa ghuzim garugha, ghuzir muziariba isa ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir biziba bar dagh ar…®ki. Egha arazir kam…®n a ofa gamir dakozim gamima, a God…®n damazim…®n zue. Ez…® Moses ghuzir ikiav…®ra itiba inigha, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®ngarim ginge, kar arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin arazim. Egha arazir kam…®n, an ofa gamir dakozim God bagha anem…®sevez…®, a God…®n bizimram oto.
\v 16 Egha Moses bulmakaun navim ko muriaba avarazir oviba bar ada inigha, an ov…®zir pumuning ko, aning…®n ovim sara inigha, an beram…®n akuar aghuim inigha bar ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuez…®, avim bar dar isia ghua m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim…®n oto.
\p 
\v 17 Egha a bulmakaun kam…®n ikiav…®ra itir as…®zir naba, kar an iniba, tuziba, ko buariba, a bar da inigha, nguibar me itim…®n azenan ghua avim gaborogha bar da tue, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Moses ami.
\p 
\v 18 Egha Moses sipsip…®n apurir kamning…®n mam inigha izi. Kar ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damuamin sipsip. Ez…® Aron uan otariba ko me uan dafariba isa sipsip…®n dapanim gis…®n da ar…®ki.
\v 19 Ez…® Moses sipsip…®n kam m…®suegha, an ghuziba inigha ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamangi.
\v 20-21 Egha a sipsip aghoragharigha, an muriaba ko an suemning deraghav…®ra da rue. A g…®n sipsip…®n dapanim ko ovim ko an as…®zir otevir maba sara inigha, bar da isa ofa gamir dakozim gat…®gha bar ada tuez…®, avim bar dar isia ghua m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim oto. Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, Moses ami. Sipsip…®n kam, kar bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa. Ikiav…®ra Itir God an mughuriam baregh, a gifuegh, egh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\p 
\v 22 Ez…® Moses sipsip…®n apurir igharazim inigha izi, sipsip…®n kam, ofan me gumazibar amut…® me ofa gamir gumazibar otivamim. Ez…® Aron uan otariba ko uan dafariba isa sipsip…®n kam…®n dapanim gar…®ki.
\v 23 Ez…® Moses sipsip m…®suegha an ghuzir muziarim inigha, Aron…®n kuarir guvim…®n itir kuarir am…®razim, ko an dafarir puzir amebar agharir guvim…®n itim, ko dagarir puzir amebar suer agharir guvim…®n itim, dagh aghui.
\v 24 Egha Moses Aron…®n otariba inigha iza, ghuzir muziariba isa, men kuarir guvibar amadaghan itir kuarir apebar am…®raziba, ko men dafarir puzir amebar dafarir guvim…®n itiba ko dagarir puzir amebar suer guvim…®n itibagh aghui. Egha sipsip…®n ghuzir ikiav…®ra itiba bar ada inigha ghua, ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamangi.
\p 
\v 25 Egha sipsip…®n oviba ini. Kar an navim ko muriam avarazir oviba, ko an puer m…®ngarim…®n itir ovir bar ekiam ini. Egha an an ov…®zir pumuning ko, aning…®n ovim sara inigha, sipsip…®n beram…®n akuar aghuim inigha, sipsip…®n buaragharir agharir guvim…®n itim ini.
\v 26 Egha Moses ghua, God…®n damazim…®n itir yis puvat…®zir bret bar iz…®vazir ak…®rar kam bagha ghua, bret…®n ruzir me yis sara tuazir puvat…®zir mam, ko plauan me oliv…®n borem sara veregha ingarizir bret…®n ruzir mam, ko oliv…®n borer ekiam avarazir bisket…®n mam ini. Egha a bret…®n kaba isa sipsip…®n oviba ko buaghagharir agharir guvim…®n itim gis…®n at…®.
\v 27 Egha g…®n dagher kaba isa Aron uan otariba ko men dafaribagh at…®z…®, me ofan kam…®n suiragha a fegha a gamiz…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ighuavamadi.
\v 28 Ez…® Moses ua dagher kaba me da da inigha, da isa ofa gamir dakozim…®n as…®zir ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim gis…®n at…®z…®, avim bizir kaba bar dar isiz…®, da bar m…®gh…®riz…® averenir k…®nim oto. Ofan kam, a gumazibar amut…® me ofa gamir gumazibar otivamin ofa. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God an mughuriam gifuegha navim an dera.
\v 29 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Moses sipsip…®n kam…®n uan dafarimning…®n an amagapam…®n itir as…®zir tuzim…®n suiragha a fegha a gamiz…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ighuavamadi. Ez…® me gumazibar amut…® me ofa gamir gumazibar otivamin ofan sipsip…®n apurim…®n akuar kam, kar Moses uab…® damamin as…®zir tuzim. Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra bizibagh ami.
\p 
\v 30 Egha Moses biziba m…®sevir oliv…®n borer muziarir maba inigha, ghuzir an ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®riam gingezir maba sara ini. Egha ghuzim, ko borem isa, Aron ko an korotiaba sara, da kavamangi. Egha an otariba ko men korotiaba sara, da kavamangi. Egha arazir kam…®n Moses, Aron ko an otaribagh amiz…®, me ko men korotiaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizibara.
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Moses ghua kamagh…®n Aron ko an otaribav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa as…®zir tuzir kam inigh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®, egh anevigh bret…®n ak…®ram…®n itim sara dam…®. God ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, Iarara dar am…®. Ak…®rar bret itir kam, me an aven bret isa gumazibagh ami me ofa gamir gumazibar otivasa ofa gami.
\v 32 Egh ia damegh iz…®vagh, as…®zir tuzir naba ko bret…®n naba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, ia avim…®n da tueght…® da bar isi m…®gh…®righ.
\v 33 Egh ia 7plan aruebar God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n azenan mangan mark…®. Ia kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®, ian dughiar ofa gamir gumaziba m…®sevir kam g…®vagham. Guizbang…®ra, arazir gumazim gamima an ofa gamir gumazibar otivamin dughiam, a 7plan arueba.
\v 34 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…®, Akar Gavgavim e m…®kemegha ghaze, Ia uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…®, arazir kaba bar dar amu. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia dagh amigha g…®fa.
\v 35 Ia arueba ko d…®magaribar God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n ik…® mang…® 7plan dughiabar tugh, egh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizibar amu. Egh ia dar amuan kogh, ia ar…®m…®ghiregham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®keme.‚Äù
\p 
\v 36 Moses…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar aven, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir kabar Aron ko an otaribav keme. Ez…® me kamagh…®ra dagh ami.
\c 9
\s1 Aron ofan mabagh ami
\p 
\v 1 Moses Aron uan otariba ko, me isa ofa gamir ingangarim bagha me at…®gha g…®fa. Ez…® dughiar namba 8 otoz…®ma, Moses d…®kavigha Aron ko an otariba ko Israelian gumazir dapanibar diaz…®, me iza uari akufa.
\v 2 Me uari akuvagha itima, a kamagh…®n Aron m…®gei, ‚ÄúBulmakaun nguzir igiar apuritam, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damus…® a inigh. Egh sipsip…®n apurir aghuir duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zitam, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damus…® a inigh iz…®. Egh n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n aning…®n ofa damu.
\v 3 Egh n…® kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav kemegh, ‚ÄòIa arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damus…® memen apuritam inigh. Egh ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramibar amus…®, bulmakaun azenir vam…®ra ititam ko sipsip…®n apurir azenir vam…®ra ititam inigh, na bagh ofa damu. Ia as…®zir aghuibara inigh, duatam men m…®karzibar ikian mark…®.
\v 4 Egh uaghan ia ofan God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamim damus…®, bulmakaun tam ko sipsip…®n apuritam inigh. Ia, as…®zir kamning ko wit tuer ofan ia oliv…®n borem sara verezim, ia aning inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damu. Dughiar kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian damazim…®n otogham, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia ofan kabar amu.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Aron ko gumazir kaba, me ghua bizir Moses me m…®kemeziba inigha, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n borogh…®n ize. Ez…® Israelian gumazamiziba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fasa iza an damazim…®n uari akuvagha tuivighav iti.
\v 6 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ia ofan kabar amut…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n angazangarir bar gavgavim ia bativam.‚Äù
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Hibru 5:1-3; 7:27\x*Egha Moses kamagh…®n Aron m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n mang…®, egh ofan arazir kuraba g…®n amangamim ko n…®n ofan bar isi m…®gh…®righamim sara damu. N…® ua bagh kamagh…®n damut…® God n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®va, gumazamizibar arazir kuraba sara g…®n amangam. Egh g…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, gumazamiziba isa izir ofaba, n…® me bagh ofa damut…® God men arazir kuraba g…®n amangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Aron ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n ghugha, bulmakaun apurir igiar kam m…®suegha, uab…® uan arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa ofa gami.
\v 9 Ez…® Aron…®n otariba a bagha as…®zir ghuziba inigha iza a gan…®ngiz…®, a uan dafarir puzim isa ghuzim garugha, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir bizibagh arigha, ghuzir naba an ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®ngarim ginge.
\v 10 Egha g…®n Aron, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan kam…®n as…®zir oviba bar ada inigha, ov…®zimning ko beram…®n akuar aghuim ini. Egha a bar da ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuez…® avim bar dar isia zuima da bar m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim oto. Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Aron ami.
\v 11 Egha an as…®zir tuziba ko iniba inigha, nguibar me itim…®n azenan ghua da tuez…®, avim bar dar isiz…® da g…®fa.
\p 
\v 12 Egha g…®n Aron ghua, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim damuasa sipsip…®n apurir kam m…®soke. Ez…® an otariba as…®zir ghuzir kaba inigha iza a gan…®ngiz…®, an ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamangi.
\v 13 Ez…® otariba as…®zir dapanim ko as…®zir otevir maba sara vaghvagha da inigha iza a gan…®ngi. Ez…® a bar ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuez…® avim bar dar isia m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim oto.
\v 14 Ez…® an as…®zir kam…®n muriaba ko an suemning sara ruegha, bar ada isa ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizir kam…®n mabagh is…®n da ar…®ki, ez…® avim bar dar isi da m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim oto.
\p 
\v 15 Egha Aron g…®n gumazamizibar ofaba inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gami. A gumazamizibar ofabar amu men arazir kuraba g…®n amangamim…®n meme inigha, a m…®suegha an ofa gami. Mati a faragha ua bagha uan arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin as…®zim…®n ofa gamiz…® mok…®n.
\p 
\v 16-17 Egha an as…®zir gumazamiziba ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim bagha inigha izezir kamning…®n mam…®n ofa gami. An amir ofan kam, arazir me zurara m…®zarazibar ofa damuamibar g…®n zui. Egha a plaua inigha wit…®n ofa damuasa a tue. A uan dafarir z…®v…®rizim…®n plauan mabar suigha, ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuez…® avim bar dar isia zuima da bar m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim oto.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 9:18 \xt Ofa Gami 3:1-11\x*Egha g…®n, Aron bulmakau ko sipsip…®n apurir gumazamiziba God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa bagha inigha izezimning m…®soke. Ez…® an otariba as…®zir kamning…®n ghuziba inigha a gan…®ngiz…®, an ofa gamir dakozim…®n 4plan m…®riabar da kavamangi.
\v 19 Egha Aron bulmakau ko sipsip…®n apurim…®n oviba bar ada ini, kar an puer m…®ngarim borogh…®ra itir ovir bar ekiam, ko navim ko muriaba avarazir oviba, ko ov…®zir pumuning, aning…®n ovim ko beram…®n akuar aghuim, a bar da ini.
\v 20 Egha me ovir kaba isa as…®zimning…®n amagapamning gat…®gha, bar da inigha ofa gamir dakozim…®n ghu. As…®zir oviba bar, Aron ofa gamir dakozim…®n da tuez…® avim bar dar isia zuima da bar m…®gh…®riz…®, averenir k…®nim oto.
\v 21 Egha a uan dafarim…®n bulmakau ko sipsip…®n amagapamning ko agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir buaragharimning…®n suiragha da fegha dagh amiz…®, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ighuavamadi. A Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt D…®boboniba 6:22-26\x*Aron ofan kaba bar dagh amigha g…®vagha, uan agharimning ghufegha, gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, God deraghv…®ra ia damu. Egha ofa gamir dakozim ategha izaghir…®.
\v 23 Egha Moses ko Aron, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven ghu. Egha aning azenan izir dughiam…®n, aning ghaze, God deraghv…®ra bar gumazamizibar amuam. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n angazangarir bar ekiam, azenim gir…®z…® gumazamiziba bar an gani.
\v 24 Ez…® zuam…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God avim amadaz…®, an ofa gamir dakozim…®n izaghir…®. Egha avim ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim ko as…®zir oviba sara bar adar isi. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar bizir kam…®n ganigha nguazim giregha, guaba nguazim m…®suegha, pamtem…®n dia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe.
\c 10
\s1 Nadap ko Abihu arazir kurabagh ami
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Aron…®n otaribar mamning Nadap ko Abihu, aning pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim tuasa uan itariba ini. Egha aning avir m…®k…®am ko pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim isa itarim gat…®gha, avir kam inigha ofan m…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ghu. Me fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n garir avim inigh izasa m…®kemezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, bizir kam a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizim puvat…®, ez…® an an aghua.
\v 2 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, zuam…®ram avim amadaz…®, a iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n bar aning…®n isiz…®, aning areme.
\v 3 \x - \xo 10:3 \xt Aisaia 52:11; Esekiel 28:22; Jon 13:31-32\x*Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n Aron m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, fom…®ra kamagh…®n ikiangs…®gha ia m…®keme, ‚ÄòGumazir nan borogh…®n iza nan ingangarim gamiba, me bar nan apengan ik…® deragh na damuva kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bar zuezim. Eght…® k…® uan gavgavim ko angazangarim gumazamizibar akagham. Eght…® me nan ziam fam.‚Äô ‚Äù Ez…® Aron akar kam baregha m…®k…®man ibura.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Moses d…®kavigha, Aron…®n ghurir afeziar dozim Usiel, an otarimning, Misael ko Elsafan, aning…®n diaz…®, aning ize. Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua rogh…®ra kagh iz…®va, uan avebamning…®n kuamning inigh, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim ategh, saghon mang…® danganir e itim…®n azenan mang…®.‚Äù
\v 5 Ez…® aning Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ghua, gumazir kuamning inigha danganir me itim…®n azenan ghu. Aning gumazir ovengezir kuamning…®n korotiaba suezir pu. Puvat…®, Misael ko Elsafan, aning…®n korotiabar suigha aning am…®k…®r…®gha azenan zui.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Moses dat…®r…®gh…®n, Aron ko an otarir igharazir pumuning, Eleasar ko Itamar, akaba me gan…®di. A kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa apangkuvir arazim…®n g…®n mang…® gumazir aremezir kamning damuan mark…®. Ia dughiaba zurara uan dapanir ar…®ziba batoghv…®ra ik…®. Ia da ateght…® da pura ikian mark…®. Ia uan apangkuvim…®n ababanim bagh, korotiaba ab…®ghan mark…®. Ia apangkuvir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia m…®sueght…®, ia ar…®m…®ghiregham. Eght…® e Israelian gumazamiziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar puv…®ram en ataram. Eght…® Israelian igharaz darasi, kar ian marazira, merara Ikiav…®ra Itir God amadazir avim…®n aremezir gumazimning bagh aziam.
\v 7 Eght…® ia God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam atagh…®raghan mark…®, ia tong ikegh. Ia fo, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizimra ikiasa oliv…®n borem ia gaghuiz…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n adarazira. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n azenan mangegh, ia ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù Ez…® me Moses…®n akam baregha, a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.
\s1 Arazir ofa gamir gumaziba damuamiba
\p 
\v 8 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Aron m…®gei,
\v 9 ‚ÄúN…® uan otariba ko, ia wain…®n d…®par onganiba amegh, nan damazim…®n, na bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven mangan mark…®. Bar markiam. Ia aven mang…®va, ia ar…®m…®ghiregham. Ia ko ian ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, arazir kam…®n g…®nt…®gh mamagh…®ra ik…®.
\v 10 Ia deraghv…®ra biziba tuis…®gh, bizir manam a nan bizim, ez…® bizir manam, a gumazamizir k…®nibar bizim. Ez…® dar tong…®n bizir manaba nan damazim…®n zuez…®, manaba m…®ze.
\v 11 Egh ia, arazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ifongeziba, a Moses m…®kemez…® a da isa Israelia gan…®ngizir kaba, ia bar dar Israelian gumazamizibar sure damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 10:12-13 \xt Ofa Gami 6:14-18\x*Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n Aron uan otarir ikiav…®ra itir pumuning Eleasar ko Itamar m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh wit tuamin ofan nar ikiav…®ra itiba inigh. Plauan kam, ia a is…® yis puvat…®zir bret…®n ingarigh. Ofan kam, a bar God…®n bizimra, a ia gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n bret…®n kam am…®.
\v 13 Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir kam…®n na m…®kemegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, wit tuer ofan nar kaba bar, da ia ko ian otaribar biziba. Ia gumazamizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha wit tuer ofa gamiba, dar tong…®n plauan kaba ini. Egh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven bret…®n kam am…®.
\v 14-15 \x - \xo 10:14-15 \xt Ofa Gami 7:30-34\x*Eght…® Israelian gumazamiziba, God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofa damus…®, as…®zim…®n amagapam…®n itir tuzim ko buaragharim ko oviba sara inigh iz…®. Eght…® ia ofa gamir gumaziba, ia amagapam…®n itir tuzim…®n suiragh da fegh dar amut…® da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ighuavamang. Egh ia g…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n oviba tuegh. Egh ofan kam…®n as…®zir tuzibar tong…®n, ia amagapam ko buaragharim inigh. Eght…® ia ko ian adarazir, guiviba ko otariba uaghara, as…®zir tuzir kamning is…® danganir God…®n damazim…®n zuezir tam…®n mang…®, aning am…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ofan kabar as…®zir otevir kamning isa, ia ko ian boribagh an…®ngi. Egh zurazurara as…®zir otevir kamning, aning ia ko ian ovavir boribar as…®zir akuamning. Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Egha g…®n Moses ghua arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damuamin meme bagha azaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúOfa gamir gumaziba manmagh…®n memen ofa damu arazir kuraba g…®n amangamim gami?‚Äù Ez…® me a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE avim…®n a tuaz…® a isigha g…®fa.‚Äù Ez…® Moses akar kam baregha, Aron…®n otarir pumuning Eleasar ko Itamar…®n atari.
\p Egha a ghaze,
\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Ofa Gami 6:24-26\x*‚ÄúManmagh amiz…® ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan kam…®n as…®zir tuzim aman aghua? Kar ofan Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua baghav…®ra m…®sevezim, egha a ia gan…®ngi, ia gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba ak…®r…®va, men arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® anemam.
\v 18 Ia ofan kam…®n ghuzim inigha purirpenim…®n Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n aven ghuzir puvat…®. Egha manmagh amiz…®, k…® ia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ia Purirpenim…®n aven as…®zir tuzir kam amezir puvat…®?‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Aron kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. Dat…®r…®gh…®ra, gumazamiziba uan arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa ko ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®di. Ez…® k…®rara, dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir kurar kaba na bativigha g…®fa. Nan gumazir pumuning areme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofan as…®zir tuzim amam, eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ti bizir kam gakuegham, o? K…® ghaze, ti puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n oregha ghaze, Aron…®n akam a dera. Ez…® an navim an am…®ra.
\c 11
\ms1 Bizir God…®n damazim…®n // zueziba ko m…®zeziba
\mr (Sapta 11--15)
\s1 As…®zir Israelia damamiba ko // as…®zir anogorogheziba
\r (God…®n Araziba 14:3-21)
\p 
\v 1-2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses ko Aron m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa, nguazir kam…®n itir as…®zibar tong…®n, as…®zir kabara, ia dar am…®.
\v 3 As…®zir kabanang: Dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning ikia, aning uaning tuiragha iti, egha da bulmakaubar m…®n graziba api, ia dar am…®.
\v 4-6 Egh ia kamelba ko ivarareba ko igh…®aba, ia dar aman mark…®. Da bulmakaubar m…®n graziba apir as…®ziba, egha dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning ikia, uaning tuiragha itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, da nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®. K…® dar aman ian anogoroke.
\v 7 Egh ia dabar aman mark…®. Dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning iti, egha uaning tuiragha ikia, bulmakaubar m…®n graziba apir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia fogh, daba da nan damazim…®n m…®ze.
\v 8 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia as…®zir kabar aman mark…®. Egh ia dar gant…® da ar…®ghir…®t…®, ia dar kuabar suighan mark…®. Bar markiam. Da nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúEgh ongarim…®n osiriba ko d…®pam…®n osiribar tong…®n, osiriba naziaba ko sighiaba uaghara ik…®t…® ia dar am…®.
\v 10 Ez…® osiriba ko bizir muziarir ongarim ko tintinibar d…®pabar itiba, da naziaba ko sighiaba uaghara puvat…®ght…®, ia fogh, da bizir bar kuraba.
\v 11 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dar aman kogh, egh dar kuabar suighan mark…®. K…® bar anogoroke. Da bizir bar kuraba.
\v 12 Ia uam oragh, angam…®ra itir bizir d…®pabar ititam, a naziaba ko sighiaba puvat…®ght…®, ia anereman mark…®. Ia bizir kabar aghuagh da atakigh.
\p 
\v 13-19 ‚ÄúEgh ia kuarazibar tong…®n kuarazir kamagh garibar aman mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, da bizir bar kurar k…® aghuaziba. Kuarazir kaba, taragiaba, m…®gh…®aba, isaba, kotkotba, poneba, ongarim…®n kuaraziba, beniba, d…®pam…®n mughamiziba, aghunabar ekiaba ko, kina aghunababa. Ia kuarazir kabar aman mark…®.
\p 
\v 20 ‚ÄúEz…® apizir suemning ko dafarimning ko av…®ziba itiba, da bizir kuraba, k…® dar anogoroke.
\v 21 Eght…® apizibar tong…®n apizir soroghafariba ikia arua uari akuriba, ia dar am…®.
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, odezir ekiaba ko doziba, ia bar dar am…®.
\v 23 Ez…® apizir sueba ko dafariba ko av…®ziba itiba, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, da bizir bar kuraba. K…® dar anogoroke.
\p 
\v 24-25 ‚ÄúAs…®zir maba uaghan, ia damut…®, ia nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Eght…® gumazitam as…®zir kabar kuabar suiragh, o aneter danganitam…®n mangam, gumazir kam nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Gumazir as…®zir kam…®n suiraghamim, a uan korotiaba ruegh, egh a nan damazim…®n m…®zegh ik…® mang…® guarat…®zim…®n tugham.
\p 
\v 26 ‚ÄúAs…®ziba, dar soroghafariba puzir pumuning ikiava, uaning tuirazir puvat…®gha, bulmakaun m…®n graziba apir puvat…®, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, as…®zir kaba, da bizir aghuiba puvat…®.
\v 27 Ez…® as…®zir soroghafarir puziba puvat…®ziba, da bar, as…®zir aghuiba puvat…®. Egh ia as…®zir katam…®n kuam…®n suiragh…®va, ia nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Egh ia kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® guarat…®zim…®n tugham.
\v 28 Eght…® gumazitam as…®zir kuar kam inigh danganir igharazim…®n mang…®gham, a uan korotiaba ruegh, nan damazim…®n m…®zeghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham. As…®zir kaba ia gamima ia m…®ze.
\p 
\v 29-30 ‚ÄúAs…®zir kaba uaghan markiam, k…® da ian anogoroke. Kar iriaba, ko kuarziba ko iper guar av…®riba.
\v 31 K…® as…®zir kaba ian anogoroke. Eght…® ia dar kuabar suigh…®va, nan damazim…®n m…®zeghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 32 Eght…® as…®zir katam aremegh, bizitam gis…®n ir…®gham, bizir kam uaghan nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. An kuam ir…®, bizir me temebar ingarizir tam o initam o bulmakaun inim…®n ingarizir initam o m…®taritam, o ingangarir manam itir bizitam, a bizir katam gis…®n ir…®gham, a nan damazim…®n bar m…®zegham. Eght…® ia a is…® d…®pam…®n a rueght…®, bizir kam nan damazim…®n m…®zeghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 33 Eght…® as…®zir m…®zezir kam…®n m…®karzim nguazir m…®nem gir…®ght…®, bizir m…®ner kam…®n itiba bar m…®zegham. Kamagh…®n, ia m…®ner kam ab…®kigh.
\v 34 Eght…® daghetaba rogh…®ra ik…®t…®, m…®ner kam…®n d…®pam dagher kabagh ireght…®, dagher kaba nan damazim…®n uaghan m…®zegham. Ez…® d…®par m…®ner kam…®n itim, a ikuvigha m…®zegha g…®fa.
\v 35 Eght…® as…®zir kam bizitam gir…®gham, bizir kam nan damazim…®n a m…®zegham. Eght…® m…®ner kam, o bretba tuer danganir me nguazim…®n ingarizir kam, ia uaghan aneb…®kigh.
\v 36 Egh as…®zir kam mozir d…®par pura nguazim…®n otivim gir…®gham, o teng…®n d…®pam gir…®gham, eght…® d…®pam nan damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. Puvat…®. Ez…® bizir manam as…®zir kam…®n m…®karzim…®n poro, a m…®zegha ikufi.
\v 37 Eght…® as…®zir katam aremegh an kuam dagher anabar oparibagh is…®n ir…®, a deragham. Dagher anabar kam, a m…®zezir puvat…®, a zueghav…®ra iti.
\v 38 Ez…® dagher anabar kam d…®pam…®n aven itima, as…®zir kam…®n kuam a gir…®, dagher anabar kaba nan damazim…®n m…®ze.
\p 
\v 39 ‚ÄúIa as…®zir k…® damasa ia m…®kemezibagh n…®ghn…®gh. Egh as…®zir kabar tam puram aremeght…®, gumazitam o amizitam an suiragham, gumazir kam o amizir kam, nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Egh a kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 40 Eght…® gumazitam as…®zir kam…®n tuzitam ame, o as…®zir kam…®n kuam ateri, a uan korotiaba ruegh. Egh a m…®zeghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\p 
\v 41 ‚ÄúEght…® ia as…®zir muziariba ko apizir nguazim…®n aruibar aman mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh, da bizir bar kuraba.
\v 42 Egh as…®zir uan navibar nguazim davariba, ko soroghafaribar aruir as…®ziba, ko as…®zir suer av…®rav…®riba itiba, da bizir aghuiba puvat…®. Eght…® ia dar aman mark…®. K…® dar ian anogoroke.
\v 43 Ia as…®zir kabar tam aman mark…®. K…® bar dar aghua. Egh ia tam amegh, ia nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Eght…® k…® dar aghuaz…® mogh…®n, k…® bar ian aghuagham.
\v 44 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, egha k…® bar zue. Eght…® ia uari is…® na danigh, nan gumazamizibar ik…®v…®ra ik…®, egh arazir kuraba ategh, arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…® nan m…®n zueghv…®ra ik…®. Ia k…® aghuazir as…®zir m…®z…®r…®zibar am…®va, nan damazim…®n m…®zeghan mark…®.
\v 45 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. K…® ian God…®n ikiasa Isip…®n kantrin aven ia inigha azenan ize. K…® uab…® bar zuez…® nan araziba bar dera. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia zuegh ik…® nan arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®.
\p 
\v 46 ‚ÄúEz…® Akar Gavgavir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n inizir kam, an as…®ziba ko, kuaraziba ko, bizir ongarim…®n aven itiba ko, apizir nguazim…®n davaribav gei.
\v 47 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia deraghv…®ra biziba tuis…®gh, bizir manam a zue, ez…® bizir manam a nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®. Egh ia angam…®ra itir bizir ia damamiba ko ia daman koghamiba, ia deraghv…®ra dagh fogh.‚Äù
\c 12
\s1 Amizim borim bategha g…®n uab…® zuer arazim
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav m…®kemegh: Amizitam navim asegh, otarim bategham, a nan damazim…®n m…®zeghv…®ra ik…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugham, mati a uan iak…®nibav sozir dughiam.
\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt Jenesis 17:12; Luk 2:21\x*Eght…® 7plan arueba g…®vaght…®, namba 8…®n aruem otoght…®, me otarir kam…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atugham.
\v 4 Amizim borim bategha ghuzir av…®rim makuri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a nan damazim…®n m…®zegh, 33plan aruebar ikegh…®va g…®n ua zuegham. Dughiar a m…®zeghv…®ra ikiamim…®n, a bizir k…® ua baghav…®ra m…®sevezir tam…®n suighan kogham. Egh a nan Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven mangan kogh, mang…® a ua zueghamin dughiam…®n tugham.
\p 
\v 5 ‚ÄúAmizim borir guivim bategh, a 14plan aruebar m…®zeghv…®ra ikiam, mati a uan iak…®nibav sozir dughiam. A uan ghuzir av…®rim makuni, kamagh…®n amiz…® a nan damazim…®n m…®zegh, ua 66plan aruebar ikegh…®va, g…®n ua zuegham.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEgh amebam ua zuegh…®va, a uan otarir iririvim o guivir iririvim g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim bagh, sipsip…®n igiar azenir vam…®ra itim inigh, egh uaghan ofan arazir kuraba g…®n amangamim bagh, kuarazir bunbam inigh. An ofan kamning is…® ofa gamir gumazim bagh God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®.
\v 7 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim amizir kam…®n kuarazim ko sipsip inigh na bagh ofa damut…®, amizim ua zuegham. Eght…® ghuzir kam amizim damut…® a ua m…®zeghan kogham. A dat…®r…®gh…®n nan damazim…®n zuegha g…®fa. Amizim otarim o guivim bategh, an arazir kamra damu.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 12:8 \xt Luk 2:24\x*‚ÄúAmizitam sipsip givezamin dag…®aba otevegh, a kuarazir bunbar igiar pumuning o os…®rvar igiar pumuning inigh iz…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir tam…®n, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damu, egh kuarazir igharazim…®n, an arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir kamning…®n ofa damight…®, amizim ua nan damazim…®n zuegham.‚Äù
\c 13
\s1 Gumazamiziba duaba isiva arazir kabar amu
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Moses ko Aron m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúGumazitam o amizitam, duatam o okatam o m…®karzir ghuarir ghurghuritam, an m…®karzim…®n otogham, egh bizir kam…®n ganganim mati lepan ar…®mariam o ar…®mariar ekiar igharaziba otivasava ami, eght…® me a inigh ofa gamir gumazim Aron bagh mang…®, o an otarir uaghan ofa gamiba, men tav bagh mang…®.
\v 3 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim deraghv…®ra duar kam…®n ganigh fogh suam, an duar kurim…®n aven itir ar…®ziba ghurghurigha g…®fa, ez…® duam bar an m…®karzim…®n aven ghu, kar lepan ar…®mariamra o ar…®mariar ekiar igharazim. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim an ganigh g…®vagh, kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòGumazir kam, a God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô
\v 4 Eght…® duam ghurghuright…®, ofa gamir gumazim duam…®n gant…®, a m…®karzim…®n inim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogh, egh ar…®zir ghurghuriba puvat…®ght…®, ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam m…®k…®m suam, a uab…®ra d…®penitam…®n ik…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh.
\v 5 Eght…® namba 7…®n aruem…®n, ofa gamir gumazim, ua gumazir kam…®n duam…®n gan a tuis…®gh, eght…® duam…®n ganganim kamagh…®ra ik…® ekeveghan koght…®, a ua gumazim ateght…® a 7plan aruebar uab…®ra ua ikegh.
\v 6 Eght…® 7plan aruer kaba g…®vaght…®, ofa gamir gumazim uam an gant…®, duar kam m…®sigh, egh ekeveghan koght…®, a fogh suam, gumazir kam pura duar k…®nim iti. Egh ofa gamir gumazim a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zue. N…® uan korotiaba ruegh, zuegh…®va mang…®.‚Äô
\v 7 Eght…® bizir kam…®n g…®n, duam ua isit…®, gumazim ua mang…® ofa gamir gumazim batogh uab…® an akagh.
\v 8 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim deraghv…®ra gumazir kam…®n duam…®n gant…®, duar kam ekeveght…®, a fogh suam, gumazir kam lepan ar…®mariar kurar ekiam iti. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam duar gavgavim ik…®t…®, me an aku ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®.
\v 10 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim deragh gumazim…®n duam…®n ganigh. Eght…® duar kam ghurghurigh, ar…®zibar amut…® da ghurghurigh aven emigh m…®zazim a gasam,
\v 11 gumazir kam lepan ar…®mariam an iti.\f + \fr 13:11 \ft Hibruia ar…®mariar kam ziar av…®ribar a d…®bori, ‚Äúlepan ar…®mariam.‚Äù Ar…®mariar kam lepan ar…®mariar e dat…®r…®gh…®n garim…®n m…®rara garir puvat…®.\f* Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n gumazim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô Ofa gamir gumazim fogha g…®fa, gumazir kam a m…®zezir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a pura gumazim ateght…®, a uab…®ra uan d…®penim…®n ikian kogham.
\v 12-13 Eght…® ar…®mariar kam bar ekevegh mang…® gumazir kam…®n m…®karzim bar anevaraght…®, ofa gamir gumazim ua gumazim…®n m…®karzim bar deraghv…®ram an gan…®va a tuis…®gham. Egh a gumazim…®n gant…®, ar…®mariar kam bar an m…®karzim inight…®, an m…®karzim bar ghurghuright…® a fogham, ar…®mariar kam g…®vasava ami, eght…® a kamagh…®n gumazim m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zue.‚Äô Ez…® kamagh…®n, gumazir kam a zuegha g…®fa.
\v 14 Eght…® g…®n, duaba bigh tuzir aven itiba azenan otivight…®, gumazir kam zueghan kogham.
\v 15 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim uam an duabar gant…®, da bight…®, a gumazir kam m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô Gumazim duaba ikia egha da b…®ghiz…® dar tuziba duar toribar otivt…®, kamagh…®n a nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®. Kamagh garir duam, a bar ar…®mariar kuram.
\v 16 Egh g…®n duam m…®sight…®, nir ghurghurim otoght…®, gumazir kam ua ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®.
\v 17 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim deragh gumazir kam…®n duam…®n gant…®, an duam m…®s…®ngight…® an inim ghurghurigham, kamagh…®n gumazir kam nan damazim…®n zuegham. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuegha g…®fa.‚Äô
\p 
\v 18 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam okam an m…®karzim…®n ik…®, egh m…®sight…®,
\v 19 egh g…®n okam ikezir danganim…®n, an m…®karzim f…®gh ghurghurigham, o an m…®karzim aghevegh ghurghuright…®, kamagh…®n gumazir kam ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…® uab…® is…® an akagh.
\v 20 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam…®n okar duam…®n danganim deragh an ganigh. Duam tong an inivaf…®zim…®n aven mang…®ght…®, an inim…®n ar…®ziba ghurghurigham, eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n gumazim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô Lepan ar…®mariar kam okar m…®s…®ngizir kam…®n danganim…®n otozim, a bizir bar kuram.
\v 21 Egh ofa gamir gumazim an gant…®, ar…®ziba ghurghurighan koght…®, duam tong an inivaf…®zim…®n aven mang…®ghan kogh, egh a tong deragh deraght…®, ofa gamir gumazim anet…®ght…® a uab…®ra ik…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh.
\v 22 Eght…® 7plan aruer kabar g…®n duar kam ik…®v…®ra ik…® ekeveght…®, ofa gamir gumazim fogh suam, an ar…®mariar bar kuram, egh kamagh…®n gumazim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô
\v 23 Eght…® duar m…®karzim…®n itim…®n ganganim kamagh…®ra ikia, egha ekevir puvat…®, kar okar kam…®n duar kurim. Kamagh…®n, ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n gumazim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zue.‚Äô
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúEght…® avim gumazitam…®n inivaf…®zim…®n isight…®, an duam ghurghurigham, o a ghurghurigh aghevegham,
\v 25 eght…® ofa gamir gumazim duar kam deragh an ganigh. A gant…®, duar kurir kam…®n ar…®ziba ghurghuright…®, duam guizbang…®ra m…®karzim…®n aven mang…®t…®, ofa gamir gumazim fogham, duar kam, a lepan ar…®mariar bar kuram. Egh a gumazim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô
\v 26 Ofa gamir gumazim an gant…®, ar…®zir duam…®n danganim…®n otiviba ghurghurighan koght…®, duam an inivaf…®zim…®n aven mangan kogh, egh m…®s…®ng damut…®, kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazim aneteght…® a uab…®ra ik…® mang…® 7plan dughiabar tugh.
