\v 29 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam o amizitam, duar muziariba an dapanim o an aghozim batoght…®,
\v 30 ofa gamir gumazim duar muziarir kaba deragh dar gant…®, duar muziariba inivaf…®zim okor bar aven mang…®t…®, ar…®zir av…®riba duar muziarir kabar danganibar puvat…®gh, egh ar…®ziba aghevegh ianguright…®, ofa gamir gumazim fogham, duar kaba da ar…®mariar bar kuram. Egh an a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô Kar dapaniba ko aghozibar otivir z…®ghz…®zir ar…®mariam.
\v 31 Ofa gamir gumazim derav…®ra an duar muziaribar gant…®, duar muziariba inivaf…®zim okor bar aven mangan koght…®, ar…®zir p…®zir aghuiba duam itir danganim…®n deragha otivighan koght…®, a gumazim o amizim ateght…® a uab…®ra ik…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh.
