\v 33 kamagh…®n gumazim o amizim uan dapanir ar…®ziba o kuar ar…®zibagh isegh, egh a duar muziariba itir danganim gisan mark…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, anet…®ght…® a uab…®ra ik…® mang…® 7plan dughiabar tugh.
