\v 45 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam duar kurar kamagh garitam ik…®, a korotiar b…®b…®zibar aghuigh, uan dapanir ar…®zim batoghan kogh, egh dafarim…®n uan akam avaragh, egh pamten kamagh…®n d…®m m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòK…® zuezir puvat…®. K…® zuezir puvat…®.‚Äô
\v 46 Gumazir ar…®mariar kamagh garim ik…®v…®ra ik…®va, nan damazim…®n zueghan kogham. A uan namakaba ategh danganir me itim…®n azenan uab…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Moses Osirizir Araziba, bizir korotiabagh amima da m…®zezibav gei
\p 
\v 47-48 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses ko Aron m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar mabar, bizir inibagh amima da ikuviba, kar lepan ar…®mariam…®n m…®n inir kabar aven itiba. Da, korotiaba ko, nir av…®zir me sipsip…®n ar…®zibar ingariziba ko, nir tret…®n aghuibar ingariziba ko, bulmakaun iniba ko, korotiar me as…®zibar inim…®n ingariziba, da dar otifi.
\v 49 Egh nir kam, ar…®mariar kurar kam an aven ik…®t…®, garim o aghevim an otoght…®, me nir kam inigh mang…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n akagh.
\v 50 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim a inigh deragh an ganigh, egh ar…®mariar kurar kam itir bizir kam is…® danganir igharazitam dat…®ght…®, a uab…®ra ik…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh.
\v 51 A namba 7…®n aruem…®n deraghv…®ra uam an gant…®, ar…®mariar kurar kam, a korotiam o inim…®n bar ekeveght…®, a fogh suam, kar lepan ar…®mariam. Ez…® korotiar kam o nir kam, a nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.
\v 52 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazim korotiar kam avim…®n a tuaght…®, a bar isigh. Bizir kam lepan ar…®mariam…®n m…®n a bato, eght…® a bar isi m…®gh…®righ.
\p 
\v 53 ‚ÄúEght…® ofa gamir gumazim deraghv…®ra korotiar kam…®n gant…®, a kamagh…®ra ik…®t…®, ar…®mariar kuram korotiar kam bar a inighan kogham,
\v 54 eght…® a me m…®kemeght…® me korotiar kam ruegh egh anet…®ght…®, a ik…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh.
\v 55 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim g…®n deraghv…®ra uam ar…®mariar bar kurar kam…®n gant…®, a korotiam…®n av…®zir manam…®n aven, o azenan otoght…®, ar…®mariar kurar kam…®n ganganim kamagh…®ra gant…®, an ganganim garim o aghevim ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, a fogh suam, a nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®. Ar…®mariar kurar kam ti ekeves, o puvat…®, kar pura bizim, ofa gamir gumazim an ek…®vamin arazim g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. A fogha g…®fa, a nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, ofa gamir gumazim, korotiam avim…®n a tuaght…® a bar isi m…®gh…®righ.
\p 
\v 56 ‚ÄúMe a rueght…®, g…®n ofa gamir gumazim deraghv…®ra uam an ganigh, bizir lepan ar…®mariam…®n m…®n garim g…®vaght…®, a korotiar av…®zir kam ab…®kigh o as…®zim…®n m…®karzir nir kam, a ikuviz…® nagh…®ra anetugh a makunigh.
