\v 58 Egh a korotiam o as…®zim…®n m…®karzim…®n inim ruer dughiam…®n, lepan ar…®mariam…®n m…®n itir puvat…®, an ghuavim ua namba 2…®n dughiam…®n a rueght…®, korotiar kam nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\p 
\v 59 ‚ÄúAr…®mariar bar kuram…®n m…®n itir bizir inibagh amima da ikuvim, Akar Gavgavir kam an gun m…®gei. Mati korotiaba ko, nir av…®zir me sipsip…®n ar…®ziba ko, nir tret…®n aghuibar ingariziba ko, bulmakaun iniba ko, korotiar me as…®zibar inibar ingariziba. Akar Gavgavir kam ghaze, korotiar kaba, da zue, o da nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\c 14
\s1 Lepan ar…®mariam g…®vaght…® zueghamin arazim
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 2 \x - \xo 14:2 \xt Matyu 8:4; Mak 1:44; Luk 5:14; 17:14\x*‚ÄúGumazir manam lepan m…®n garir ar…®mariar kuram an iti, kar Arazir Moses Osirizim. An ar…®mariam g…®vaghamin dughiam…®n, a nan damazim…®n zueghs…®, me a inigh ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®.
\v 3 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim a inigh danganir me itim…®n azenan mang…®, egh deragh an m…®karzim…®n ganigh. Eght…® lepan m…®n garir ar…®mariam guizbang…®ra bar g…®vaght…®,
\v 4 ofa gamir gumazim me m…®kemeght…®, me nan damazim…®n kuarazir angam…®ra ikia zuezir pumuning, ko sidan temer otevitam, ko benir aghevir tam, ko temer hisop…®n aguatam, da inigh iz…®.
\v 5 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim me m…®kemeght…®, me nguazir m…®netam inigh daghurir aghuitam…®n mang…® d…®par igiar d…®k…®riatam tuigh, a inigh iz…®. Egh me g…®n kuarazir kamning…®n tam inigh, m…®nem gis…®n an suiragh a m…®sueght…®, an ghuzim m…®nem…®n mag…®r…®.
\v 6 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir igharazim ko temer sidan otevir kam, ko benir aghevir kam, ko hisop…®n aguam is…® ghuzim itir d…®pam darugh, zuam…®ram anesigh.
\v 7 Egh gumazir kam nan damazim…®n zueghs…®, me 7plan dughiabar d…®par ghuzim itim a gis…®n a kavamang. Egh ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n damazim…®n zuegha g…®fa.‚Äô Egh ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir angam…®ra itim inigh, nguibam…®n azenan mang…®, egh dadaba itir danganim…®n aneteght…® a m…®ghegh mang…®.
\v 8 Gumazim zueghs…® a uan korotiam ruva, dapanir ar…®ziba ko uan m…®karzim…®n ar…®ziba bar dagh isegh uab…® ruegh. A kamagh…®n damigh, nan damazim…®n zuegh, egh nguibam…®n aven mang…®, egh 7plan aruebar a uan purirpenim…®n azenan ik…®.
\v 9 Egh aruer namba 7…®n, gumazir kam ua, uan dapanir ar…®ziba bar dagh is…®va, ghuamas…®ziba ko sevanir ar…®ziba, ko namnam…®n ar…®zir maba sara isegh, egh a uab…® ruva uan korotiam sara ruegh, egh nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúEgh namba 8…®n dughiam…®n, a sipsip…®n apurir pumuning ko sipsip…®n amebar azenir vam…®ra itim inigh. Da bar deragh egh duatam dar m…®karzibar ikian kogham. Egh a wit tuamin ofan m…®n, a 3 kilogrem…®n plauan aghuiba ko oliv…®n borem sara da veregh da inigh. Egh oliv…®n borer itarir pumuning gingegh.
\v 11 Egh a sipsipba ko plaua ko oliv…®n borem inigh na bativamin Purirpenim…®n iz…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazitam an akuraght…® a zuegham. Ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam ko ofan kaba sara a inigh, na bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n iz…®, nan damazim…®n tugham.
\v 12 Egh dat…®r…®gh…®n ofa gamir gumazim sipsip…®n apurir kamning…®n tam inigh oliv…®n borem sara ofa damu, mati an os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa. A faragh bizir kaba dafarim…®n dar suiragh da fegh dar amut…® da nan damazim…®n ighuavamang…®.
\v 13 Ofa gamir gumazim sipsip…®n kam is…®, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba bagha me bulmakaubav sozir danganim…®n mang…® a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Guizbang…®ra, os…®mt…®zim agevir ofaba, da arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofabar m…®rara ghu. Kar nan bizimra, ez…® k…® God, k…® a isa ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n damuam.
\v 14 Egh g…®n ofa gamir gumazim sipsip…®n ghuzir taba inigh, gumazim…®n kuarir guvim…®n itir kuarir apebam…®n am…®razim dat…®gh, egh an agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir dafarir puzir amebam ko gumazir kam…®n dagarir amebar agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itim dat…®gh.
\v 15 Egh ofa gamir gumazim oliv…®n borem…®n taba inigh uan dafarir k…®riam gingegh, egh borer kam dafarim…®n an suiragh.
\v 16 Egh a uan agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir dafarir puzir bizibar akakazim is…®, uan dafarir k…®riam…®n itir borer kam darugh, egh 7plan dughiabar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a kavamang.
\v 17 Egh g…®n ofa gamir gumazim borer an dafarim…®n ikiav…®ra itir taba inigh, gumazir zueghamim…®n kuarir guvim…®n itir kuarir apebam…®n am…®razim dat…®gh, egh uaghan oliv…®n borem is…® gumazir kam…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir dafarir puzir amebam ko gumazir kam…®n dagarir amebar agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itim dat…®gh, danganir kaba, a faragha ghuziba dagh ar…®ki.
\v 18 Egh borer nar ofa gamir gumazim…®n dafarim…®n ikiav…®ra itiba, gumazir kam…®n dapanim gingegh. Arazir kam…®n a gumazim damight…®, a nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúEgh ofa gamir gumazim ofan arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin as…®zim…®n ofa damut…®, gumazim nan damazim…®n zuegham. Egh a g…®n, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damus…®, as…®zim m…®sogham.
\v 20 Egh an as…®zir kam, wit tuer ofa sara, ofa gamir dakozim…®n ofa damu. Egh arazir kam…®n ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damut…®, gumazim nan damazim…®n bar zuegham.
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazim uab…® zueghs…® bizir ofa damuamibagh ivezamin dag…®aba puvat…®gh, a sipsip…®n nguzir apurir vam…®rara inigh. Sipsip…®n kam a gumazim…®n os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa. Eght…® g…®n ofa gamir gumazim an suiragh a fegh a damut…® a nan damazim…®n ighuavamang…®. Gumazir kam, 1 kilogrem plauan aghuim uaghan a inigh, oliv…®n borem sara a veregh wit tuer ofa damu. Egh a oliv…®n borer aghuir itarir pumuning v…®raram aning…®n suiragh iz…®.
\v 22 A dag…®aba otevegh sipsipbagh ivezan iburagh, a kuarazir bunbar pumuning inigh ofa damus…® iz…®. Egh kuarazir tam arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damuva, egh kuarazir igharazim, bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa damu.
\v 23 Namba 8…®n aruem…®n, gumazir kam uab…® zueghs…®, bizir kaba bar ada inigh nan damazim…®n ofa gamir gumazim bagh na bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n mang…®.
\v 24 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa bagh sipsip…®n nguzir kam ko oliv…®n borem inigh, dafarim…®n an suiragh a fegh a damut…® a nan damazim…®n ighuavamang…®.
\v 25 Egh ofa gamir gumazim os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa bagh sipsip…®n nguzir kam m…®suegh, egh ofan ghuzir taba inigh, gumazir uab…® zus…® damuamin gumazir kam…®n kuarir guvim…®n itir kuarir apebam…®n am…®razim dat…®gh, egh an agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir dafarir puzir amebam ko gumazir kam…®n dagarir amebar agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itim dat…®gh.
\v 26 Egh ofa gamir gumazim oliv…®n borer taba inigh uan dafarir k…®riam gingegh, egh borer kam dafarim…®n an suiragh.
\v 27 Egh a uan agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir dafarir puzir akakazim is…®, uan dafarir k…®riam…®n itir borer kam darugh, egh 7plan dughiabar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a kavamang.
\v 28 Egh g…®n ofa gamir gumazim borer an dafarim…®n ikiav…®ra itir taba inigh, gumazir zueghamim…®n kuarir guvim…®n itir kuarir apebam…®n am…®razim dat…®gh, egh uaghan oliv…®n borem is…® gumazir kam…®n agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itir dafarir puzir amebam ko gumazir kam…®n dagarir amebar agharir guvim…®n amadaghan itim dat…®gh, danganir kaba, a faragha ghuziba dagh ar…®ki.
\v 29 Egh borer nar ofa gamir gumazim…®n dafarim…®n ikiav…®ra itiba, gumazir kam…®n dapanim gingegh. Egh arazir kam…®n a gumazim damight…®, a nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\v 30 Egh ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir kam kuarazir bunbar ofa damuasa inigha izezimning, an aning inigh.
\v 31 A kuarazir tam, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu, egh igharazim an ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damu. Egh a uaghan wit tuer ofa ko kuarazir bunbar kamning sara ofa damu. Arazir kam…®n ofa gamir gumazim, gumazir nan damazim…®n zueghamin kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…® ofa damu.
\v 32 Arazir kam, gumazir uan lepan m…®n garir ar…®mariam ag…®vs…®, egh dag…®aba otevegh, ofan as…®zibagh ivezan iburagham, an arazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®va, nan damazim…®n zuegham.‚Äù
\s1 Ar…®mariar kuram d…®penim damight…® d…®penim ikuvighamim
\p 
\v 33 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Moses ko Aron m…®gei,
\v 34 ‚ÄúIa g…®n Kenan…®n nguazim…®n mangegh an ikiam, nguazir k…® ia dan…®ngamin kam, a ian nguazimra ikiam. Egh dughiar ia Kenan…®n ikiamim, k…® ti lepan m…®n garir ar…®mariar kuram damight…®, a d…®penir tabar amut…® da ikuvigham.
\v 35 Eght…® d…®penir ghuavim mang…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòK…® as…®ghas…®zir mam ar…®mariar kuram…®n m…®n an gari an nan d…®penim…®n otogha nan d…®penim gas…®ghas…®si.‚Äô
\v 36 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n oregh…®va, gumazim m…®k…®mt…®, a d…®penim…®n aven itir biziba bar da ater azenan mangam. Eght…® gumazim kamagh…®n damighan koght…®, ofa gamir gumazim iz…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòBizir d…®penim…®n aven ikiav…®ra itir kaba bar God…®n damazim…®n ikuvigha m…®ze, ez…® a dar anogoroke.‚Äô Eght…® gumazim biziba bar da inigh azenan mang…®t…®, ofa gamir gumazim aven mang…® d…®penim…®n ganam.
\v 37 A bar deraghv…®ra bizir d…®penim…®n b…®ribagh ami da ikuvim…®n ganam. Egh a gant…®ma, bizir gariba ko agheviba torir muziariba b…®ribar ar…®ght…® a suam, bizir kam bar b…®ribar aven ghu,
\v 38 egh ofa gamir gumazim azenan mang…®gh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòD…®penir kam, a 7plan dughiabar pura ikiam.‚Äô
\v 39 Egh dughiar namba 7…®n, ofa gamir gumazim ua iz…® d…®penim getiv an ganam. Eght…® as…®ghas…®zir kam b…®rim…®n otogh bar ekeveght…®,
\v 40 ofa gamir gumazim me m…®kemeght…®, me bizir kurar kam itir dag…®aba asigh, egh nguibam…®n azenan mang…® danganir me ghua bizir m…®z…®r…®zir nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®ziba makuri nagh…®n, da makunigh.
\v 41 Me dar amigh g…®vagh, nguazir m…®s…®ngizir dag…®ar d…®penim…®n aven b…®riba bar da avarazim angarigh. Egh da inigh nguibam…®n azenan mang…®, danganir bizir kuraba akurir nagh…®ra da kunigh.
\v 42 Egh me dag…®ar igiaba inigh dag…®ar kabar danganibar ar…®gh, ua b…®rir kabar ingarigh. Egh nguazir kumkuar igiam inigh d…®penim…®n b…®riba ua dar aghu da avegh.
\p 
\v 43 ‚ÄúEght…® me ingangarir kam damight…®, an g…®n as…®ghas…®zir kam ua b…®rim…®n otoght…®,
\v 44 ofa gamir gumazim ua d…®penim…®n mang…®, egh deraghv…®ra a getiv an ganigh. As…®ghas…®zir kam otogh bar ekevegh d…®penim damight…® a ikuvigh, egh d…®penir kam a nan damazim…®n m…®zegha g…®fa.
\v 45 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me d…®penir kam ap…®righ dag…®aba ko temeba bar ada angarigh. Egh me da inigh nguibam…®n azenan mang…®, danganir me nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®zir biziba makuri nagh…®n da makunigh.
\p 
\v 46 ‚ÄúEgh d…®penir m…®zezir kam, gumazitam an aven mang…®, a nan damazim…®n m…®zegh…®va kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 47 Eght…® gumazitam d…®penir kam…®n aven dam…®, o an aven dakuam, kamagh…®n a uan korotiaba ruegh.
\p 
\v 48 ‚ÄúEght…® ofa gamir gumazim ua iz…® d…®penim…®n gant…®, an b…®riba deragham, eght…® as…®ghas…®zir kam uam a batoghan koght…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòD…®penir kam a God…®n damazim…®n zue.‚Äô A fo, bizir lepan ar…®mariar kuram…®n m…®n garir d…®penibagh as…®ghas…®zir kam, a ua itir puvat…®. As…®ghas…®zir kam, a g…®fa.
\v 49 Arazir d…®penim gamima a ua nan damazim…®n zuezim, a kamak…®n. Ofa gamir gumazim me m…®kemeght…®, me nan damazim…®n kuarazir angam…®ra ikia zuezir pumuning, ko sidan temer otevir tam, ko benir aghevir tam, ko temer hisop…®n aguatam, inigh iz…®.
\v 50 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim me m…®kemeght…®, me nguazir m…®netam inigh daghurir aghuitam…®n mang…® d…®par igiar d…®k…®riam tuigh, a inigh iz…®. Egh g…®n ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir kamning…®n tam inigh, m…®nem gis…®n an suiragh a m…®sueght…® an ghuzim m…®nem…®n mag…®r…®.
\v 51 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir angam…®ra itir igharazim ko temer sidan otevir kam, ko benir aghevir kam, ko hisop…®n aguam da is…® ghuzim itir d…®pam darugh, egh zuam…®ra da asigh. Egh g…®n 7plan dughiabar d…®par ghuzim itim d…®penim…®n a kavamang.
\v 52 Ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n damut…® d…®penim nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\v 53 Egh ofa gamir gumazim kuarazir angam…®ra itim inigh, nguibam…®n azenan mang…®, egh dadaba itir danganim…®n aneteght…® a m…®ghegh mang…®. Kar d…®penim…®n m…®z…®r…®ziba agevir arazim, eght…® d…®penim nan damazim…®n ua zuegham.
\p 
\v 54-56 ‚ÄúArazir kaba, da gumazamizir ar…®mariar kuraba itiba ko gumazamizir duar muziariba itiba ko, okaba ko duar m…®karzim…®n otiviba, ko as…®ghas…®zir korotiaba ko d…®penibagh amima da nan damazim…®n m…®zeziba, da bizir m…®z…®r…®zir kabanang…®n ia m…®gei.
\v 57 Akar Gavgavir kaba, da ian akaght…® ia fogh suam, bizir manaba nan damazim…®n zue, ez…® bizir manaba zuezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\c 15
\s1 M…®karzim…®n otivir m…®z…®r…®zir mabar Akar Gavgaviba
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses ko Aron m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® Israelian gumazamiziba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam:
\p ‚ÄúGumazitam, an m…®karzir mogomem duam a batoght…® ghuzir m…®t…®zim an azenan otivt…®, egh ghuzir m…®t…®zir kam a damut…®, a nan damazim…®n m…®zegham.
\v 3 Egh duam…®n ghuzir m…®t…®zir kam, an m…®karzir mogomem…®n akam…®n otivam, o bizir kam gavgavigh d…®pam ivemarir tuavim ap…®right…®, gumazir kam nan damazim…®n m…®zegham.
\v 4 Eght…® danganir an apiaghiriba o akuiba, da bar m…®zegham.
\v 5-6 Tina gumazir kam…®n m…®siam…®n suiragham, o an apiaghiri bizitam daperagh, kamagh…®n a uan korotiaba ru, egh d…®pam…®n uab…® ruegh, egh nan damazim…®n m…®zegh ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 7 Eght…® gumazir manam o amizim uan dafarim is…® gumazir duar kam itim…®n m…®karzim…®n suiragh, a uan korotiaba ru egh uab…® ruegh, egh m…®zegh ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 8 Eght…® gumazir duar kam itim, a gumazir nan damazim…®n zuezim giparight…®, gumazir kam uaghan m…®zegh, uan korotiam ru, egh uab…® ruegh m…®zegh ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 9 Eght…® gumazir duar kam itim, an hoziam gis…®n itir dabirabim daperagham, eght…® bizir kam uaghan m…®zegham.
\v 10 Eght…® gumazitam uan dafarim…®n gumazir kam aperazir dabirabim…®n suiragham, a uaghan m…®zegh, ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham. Eght…® gumazitam gumazir bizir an gaperaghav ikezim inigh aneter mangam, a uaghan uan korotiam ru egh uab…® ruegh, egh a m…®zegh ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 11 Eght…® gumazir duar kam itim faragh uan dafariba rueghan kogh, egh gumazir igharazim…®n suiraght…®, gumazir igharazir kam uan korotiam ruegh egh d…®pam…®n bar uab…® ruegh, egh a m…®zegh…®va ik…®v…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 12 Eght…® gumazir duar kam itim, nguazir m…®ner tam…®n suiraght…®, kamagh…®n, me m…®ner kam ab…®kigh. Egh a uan dafarim…®n temer itarim…®n suiraght…®, kamagh…®n, me itarir kam deragh d…®pam…®n a ruegh.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir kam…®n duar m…®t…®zir d…®paba itim g…®vaght…®, a 7plan dughiabar ikegh zuegham. Egh a mang…® uan korotiam ruegh, egh d…®par aghuim guruegh, egh nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\v 14 Eght…® namba 8…®n dughiam otoght…®, a kuarazir bunbar pumuning inigh mang…® God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tugh…®va, kuarazir bunbar pumuning is…® ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngigh.
\v 15 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, kuarazir kamning…®n tam is…® arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu, egh kuarazir igharazim is…® ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damu. Arazir kam…®n, a gumazir kam…®n akuraght…®, an m…®z…®r…®zim g…®vaght…®, gumazim ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n zuegham.
\p 
\v 16 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam, d…®pam puram an m…®karzir mogomem…®n otivt…®, a m…®zegham, a uan m…®karzim bar d…®pam…®n a ruegh, egh ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 17 Eght…® d…®par kam an korotiam o inim o as…®zibar inibar ingarizir bizitam gireght…®, a d…®pam…®n a ruegh, eght…® bizir kam m…®zegh ik…®v…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\p 
\v 18 ‚ÄúGumazim amizim ko dakuigh, egh aning m…®zegham. Aning uaning ko akuigha g…®vazir dughiam…®n, aning mang…® d…®pam…®n ruegh, egh aning m…®z…®r…®zim sara m…®zeghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúAmizim uan iak…®nibav sozir dughiam…®n, a m…®z…®r…®zim sara ik…® mang…®t…® 7plan arueba gevegham. Eght…® gumazitam o amizitam an suiragh, a m…®z…®r…®zim sara kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 20 Eght…® dakozir an akuim ko an apiaghirir biziba, da bar m…®zegham.
\v 21-23 Gumazitam o amizitam dafarim is…® an dakozim o bizir an apiav ikezibar suiragh, a m…®zegham. Egh a uan korotiam ruegh egh d…®pam…®n bar uab…® ruegh, egh a m…®zegh ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 24 Eght…® gumazitam, amizir uan iak…®nibav sozir dughiam…®n a ko dakut…®, amizir kam…®n m…®z…®r…®ziba an ik…® mang…® 7plan dughiabar tugham. Eght…® dakozir manam gumazim a dakuam, a uaghan m…®zegham.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúAmizitam uan iak…®nibav sozir dughiam batozir puvat…®gha pura dughiar igharazir mabar ghuzim bati, o an iak…®nibav sozir dughiam ikiav…®ra itima a ghuzim bata dughiar ruarim…®n ghuav…®ra iti, kamagh…®n a m…®z…®r…®zim sara ik…® mang…®t…®, ghuzim bar g…®vagham.
\v 26 Egh a dughiar kam…®n dakozir manam gakui, o dabirabir manam gaperaghav ike, bizir kaba uaghan m…®zegham.
\v 27 Eght…® gumazitam o amizitam bizir an apiav kezitam…®n suiragham, a uaghan m…®zegham. A uan korotiaba ruegh, egh d…®pam…®n bar uab…® ruegh. Egh a m…®z…®r…®zim sara ik…® mang…®t…®, aruem mag…®r…®gham.
\v 28 Amizim…®n ghuzim g…®vaght…®, a 7plan dughiabar ikegh nan damazim…®n zuegham.
\v 29 Eght…® namba 8…®n dughiam otoght…®, a kuarazir bunbar pumuning inigh iz…®, egh mang…® na bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngigh.
\v 30 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, kuarazir kamning…®n tam is…® arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu, egh kuarazir igharazim is…® ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim damu. Eght…® arazir kam…®n, an amizir kam…®n akuraght…®, an m…®z…®r…®zim g…®vaght…®, a ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n zuegham.
\p 
\v 31 ‚ÄúGua kamagh…®ra, Akar Gavgavir kamra Israelia dan…®ngigh. Me nan damazim…®n m…®zegha itir dughiam…®n, me uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan. Me uan m…®z…®r…®ziba bar dar saghon ik…®. Nan Purirpenim men tong…®n iti, eght…® me m…®z…®r…®ziba sara ik…®va, an aven mangan mark…®. Puvat…®ght…® me nan Purirpenim damut…® a m…®zegham. Me kamagh…®n damut…®, k…® me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Akar Gavgavir kaba, gumazim o amizim…®n m…®karzim duaba a batifi, ez…® gumazim amizim ko akuima an d…®pam an m…®karzim gire, bizir kam aning gamima aning nan damazim…®n m…®ze, kar an Akar Gavgaviba.
\v 33 Egha Akar Gavgavir kaba, amizibar iak…®nir ar…®mariam m…®gei. Egha a gumazitam ko amizitam ghuzir m…®t…®zim men m…®karzir mogomem bato, Akar Gavgavir kam me m…®gei. Egha uaghan gumazir amizir m…®z…®r…®zim sara itim koma akuim m…®gei.
\c 16
\ms1 Dughiar Ekiar God Gumazamizibar Arazir Kuraba G…®n Amadim
\mr (Sapta 16)
\s1 Ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim ofa gamua gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadi
\p 
\v 1 Aron…®n otarir pumuning faragha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batuegha, a bagh ofa damuasa an borogh…®n zui. Ez…® an aning m…®soghez…® aning aremegha g…®fa, ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 16:2 \xt Hibru 6:19\x*‚ÄúN…® uan avebam Aron m…®kemegh. A zurara nan purirpenim…®n aven nir ekiam…®n ak…®rang…®n Danganir Bar Anogoroghezim…®n pura mang…®va, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiar asuam…®n guam…®n tuivan mark…®. K…® ghuariar mam…®n tong…®n ik…®, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n asuam gis…®n ikiam, kar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir danganim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uab…® dughiam at…®ght…®, an an aven mang…®. A pura danganir kam…®n aven mang…®ght…®, k…® a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.
\v 3 \x - \xo 16:3 \xt Hibru 9:7\x*Aron Danganir Bar Anogoroghezim…®n aven mang…®s…®, a faragh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa bagh bulmakaun apurir igiatam inigh, egh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim bagh sipsip…®n apuritam inigh.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúAron faragh deraghv…®ra d…®pam…®n uab…® ruegh, egh g…®n korotiar kabar aghu, kar korotiar k…® uab…® ofa gamir gumaziba bagha m…®seveziba, ez…® da bar zue. Korotiar kaba bar, me deraghav…®ra nir ghurghurir aghuim…®n dar ingari. Aron ruegh g…®vagh, egh ofa gamir gumazim…®n korotiar ruarir azenan itim arugh, egh an aven azuir trausiziar otevim arugh. Egh inir ruarim is…® uan ivariam gikegh, egh inir dapanir asuar ruarim uan dapanim gighuigh a ikegh.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 16:5-6 \xt Ofa Gami 9:7; Hibru 5:1-3; 7:27-28; 9:7\x*‚ÄúEght…® Israelian gumazamiziba ofan arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa bagh, memen apurir pumuning inigh, egh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim bagh sipsip…®n apurir vam…®ra inigh iz…® Aron danight…®, a da iniam.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEgh Aron uab…® inizir bulmakaun apurir kam…®n ofa damu, egh uan arazir kuraba ko an adarazir arazir kuraba g…®n amang.
\p 
\v 7 ‚ÄúEgh a g…®n memen apurir kamning inigh mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n iz…® nan damazim…®n tugh.
\v 8 Egh a dag…®ar pumuning inigh, mam…®n osizirim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòKar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa‚Äô ez…® igharazim…®n osizirim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòKar Asasel…®n ofa.‚Äô Egh a dag…®ar pumuning modogh, egh vaghvagh aning…®n akakagham, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh memen tam am…®sevegh, egh tam asem Asasel bagh anem…®sefegh.\f + \fr 16:8 \ft Hibrun akam, akar kam deragha m…®geir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, Asasel, a Satan…®n ziam, o duar kurar mam. Ez…® marazi ghaze, kar danganir m…®s…®ngizim…®n danganir kurar mam. Ez…® marazi kamagh…®n akar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® danganitam…®n anemadagh.‚Äù\f*
\v 9 Egh Aron memen Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha m…®sevezir kam inigh, egh ofan m…®n gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu.
\v 10 Egh an asem Asasel bagha inabazir memen kam m…®soghan mark…®. Aron a inigh nan damazim…®n iz…®. Egh a memen kam, asem Asasel bagh gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n anemadagh. Eght…® memen kam gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ater mangam.
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúAron ofan kabagh amua arazir kuraba g…®n amadir dughiam…®n, an arazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®. A faragh bulmakaun kam inigh egh an aku iz…®, a m…®suegh uan arazir kuraba ko an adarazir arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu.
\v 12-13 Egh a g…®n m…®netam inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n itir ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, egh avir m…®k…®ar isia itiba m…®nem daghuigh, da inigh inir ekiam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n itir Danganir Bar Anogoroghezim…®n mang…®. Egh a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dafarir pumuning pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim a daghuigh, a is…® avir kam dat…®ght…®, pauran kam…®n m…®gharim, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n asuam avaragham, kar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir danganim. M…®gharir gavgavir kam ik…®t…®, kamagh…®n Aron uab…®, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir danganim…®n ganan kogham. An an ganight…®, k…® a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.
\v 14 Egh a bulmakaun apurim…®n ghuzitaba inigh, uan dafarir puzim a darugh Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n p…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amadir danganim…®n guam…®n a kavamang. Egh 7plan dughiabar kamagh…®ra ua ghuzir taba uan dafarir puzim…®n da inigh, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n guam…®n da kavamang.
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 16:15 \xt Hibru 9:12\x*‚ÄúEgh g…®n a gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa bagh memen kam m…®suegham. Egh a memen ghuziba inigh, purirpenim…®n aven inir ekiam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n mang…®, egh ghuzir muziarir taba Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n asuam…®n p…®n itir arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin danganim, a gis…®n da kavamangam. Egh taba is…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n guam…®n da kavamang, mati a faragha bulmakaun ghuzibagh amiz…® mok…®n.
\v 16 Egh arazir kam…®n a Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim damight…®, a nan damazim…®n zuegham. Guizbang…®ra, Israelian gumazamiziba arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amua nan akaba batuegha, arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami, ez…® arazir kam Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim gamima, a m…®ze. Na bativamin Purirpenim men tong…®n iti, ez…® men arazir kurar kaba da Purirpenim…®n bizibagh amima, da bar nan damazim…®n m…®ze. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Aron ghuzitaba inigh, na bativamin Purirpenim…®n danganir igharazibar kamagh…®ra dar amigh. Mati a faragha Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim gamiz…® mok…®n. Arazir kamra, a Purirpenim damut…® a ua zuegham.
