\v 30 ‚ÄúIa Akar Gavgavir k…® ia gan…®dir kam…®n g…®n mang…®. Gumazamizir ian faragha ghua nguazir kam…®n ikia amizir arazir bar kurir k…® bar aghuaziba, ia dar amuan mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damigham, ia nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Ia oragh. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù
\c 19
\s1 God ifongezir Arazir kaba, Israelia dar g…®n mang…®
