\v 1-2 \x - \xo 19:1-2 \xt Ofa Gami 11:44-45; 1 Pita 1:16\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Israelia m…®k…®masa Moses m…®keme:
\p ‚ÄúK…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® arazir kurabar saghon ikiava, bar zue. Kamagh…®n, ia uaghan nan m…®n arazir kurabar saghon ik…®, bar zuegh, egh nan gumazamizibara ik…®.
