\v 5 ‚ÄúIa na ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofa damus…®, ia arazir k…® ia gan…®dir kam…®n g…®n mang…®, ofan kam damu. Egh ia kamagh…®n damut…®, k…® ian ofa gifuegham.
\v 6 Ia as…®zim m…®soghezir dughiamra ofan as…®zir tuzibar am…®, o am…®mzaraghan dar am…®. Eght…® as…®zir tuzir naba dughiar m…®kezim…®n ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, ia da tueght…® da bar isi mang…® averenir k…®nim…®n otogh.
\v 7 Eght…® gumazitam dughiar m…®kezim…®n as…®zir kam am…®t…®, arazir kam nan damazim…®n bar deraghan koght…®, k…® uaghan bar an ofan kam…®n aghuagham.
\v 8 Gumazitam dughiar m…®kezim…®n as…®zir tuzir kam ame, a bizir bar zuezir me na gan…®ngizim gamima, a ikufi. Ez…® a uab…® uan arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim ik…® ivezir kuram iniam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uan gumazamizibar tong…®n a batuegham.
