\v 13 \x - \xo 19:13 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:14-15\x*‚ÄúIa paz…® gumazir igharazim damuva, egh an biziba ok…®man mark…®. Ia dag…®aba bagh ingangarim gumazitam danigh, egh ia an ingangarim…®n ivezim…®n dughiar a ingarizir kam…®n ivezim a dan…®ngigh. Ia ivezim…®n suiragh ik…® gurumzaraghan a dan…®ngan kogham.
