\v 15 \x - \xo 19:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:6-8; God…®n Araziba 16:19\x*‚ÄúIa kotiam barazir dughiam…®n, ia deraghv…®ra kotiam tuis…®gh. Egh ia deraghv…®ra kotiam ak…®righ. Ia onganarazir gumazamizibar akurvaghan mark…®, me kotiam puram a gafiragham. Egh ia gumazamizir ziaba ko gavgaviba itibar atiating men akurvaght…®, me pura kotiam gafiraghan mark…®.
