\v 19 \x - \xo 19:19 \xt God…®n Araziba 22:9-11\x*‚ÄúIa nan arazir k…® ifongezir kabar g…®n mang…®. Egh ia as…®zir igharagha garimning ateght…®, aning uaning ko dakuva nguziba batan mark…®. Egh ia dagher anabar igharagha garir pumuning azenir vam…®ran da oparan mark…®. Egh ia pura nir me tret…®n k…®nim…®n isamizim ko tret…®n me sipsip…®n ar…®zim…®n isamizim, aning isafuragha korotiar ingarizim aghuan mark…®. Kar arazir anogorogheziba.
