\v 20 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazitam ingangarir amizir k…®nitam ik…®, egh a gumazir igharazim bagh amizir kam amangasa akam ak…®ri, ez…® gumazim a givezezir puvat…®. Eght…® gumazir amizir kam…®n garim, amizir kam ko dakut…®, ia aning inigh kotiam…®n mang…®. Egh ia aning m…®sueght…®, aning aremeghan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, amizir kam a gumazir an garim…®n ingangarir amizir k…®nim.
