\v 22 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zim agevir ofa damuva gumazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amangam. Eght…® k…® an ganigh an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.
