\v 26 \x - \xo 19:26 \xt Jenesis 9:4; Ofa Gami 7:26-27; 17:10-14; God…®n Araziba 12:16; 12:23; 15:23; 18:10\x*‚ÄúIa as…®zir tuzir ghuzim itibar aman mark…®. Egh ia imezibagh amir araziba ko kukunir araziba, ia dar amuan mark…®. Da nan gavgavim…®n izezir puvat…®.
\v 27-28 \x - \xo 19:27-28 \xt Ofa Gami 21:5; God…®n Araziba 14:1\x*Ia gumazim o amizir aremezim g…®n…®ghn…®gh dapanir ar…®zir ian kuaribar borogh…®n itiba ap…®ran mark…®, egh uan ghuamas…®zibagh is…® da ot…®van mark…®. Egh ia uaghan uarir akurvaghs…®, gumazim o amizir aremezim g…®n…®ghn…®gh, uan m…®karzibar ghor, d…®ghoribar amuan mark…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia arazir kabar amuan, k…® anogoroke.
