\c 20
\s1 God gumazamizir akaba batozibagh as…®ghasigham
\p 
\v 1-2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian gumazamizibav k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\p ‚ÄúIsraelian tav o ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir Israel…®n kantrin aven itibar tav, uan borim is…® asem Molek bagh ofan m…®n a dan…®ngt…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar d…®kavigh dag…®aba is…® gumazir kam ginivight…® an aremegh.
\v 3 Gumazim borim isa Molek gan…®dir arazir kam, nan Purirpenim gamima a m…®zegha bar nan ziar ekiam d…®kab…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® gumazir kam…®n apanim damuva uan gumazamizibar tong…®n a batuegham.
\v 4 Nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba gumazir kam…®n arazir kurar kam…®n gan…®va m…®k…®m suam, kar pura bizim, egh a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan koght…®,
\v 5 kamagh…®n k…® uab…® an apanim damuva an adarazi sara, ko gumazamizir ak…®rim na gasaragha asem Molek…®n ziam feba bar, k…® men apanim damuam. K…® uan gumazamizibar tong…®n me batuegham.
