\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam na tegh, kukunir gumaziba ko, ariaghirezir gumazibar duaba ko m…®geiba bagh mang…®, a mati tuavim…®n amizim tintinibar arua gumazir igharaziba koma akui. Kamagh…®n, k…® gumazir kam…®n apanim damuva uan gumazamizibar tong…®n a batuegham.
\v 7 Ia bar zuegh ik…®, egh arazir aghuir vorogh…®ra itir k…® ifongezibar aven daru. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa.
\v 8 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ua bagha ia m…®sevez…® ia bar nan gumazamizir aghuibar otifi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, arazir k…® ifongeziba, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®.
