\v 9 \x - \xo 20:9 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:17; Matyu 15:4; Mak 7:10\x*‚ÄúEgh gumazim o amizim uan afeziam o amebam akar kuram…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, God n…® gas…®ghasigham, eght…® ia gumazir kam o amizir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Gumazim o amizir akar kam m…®kemezim, a uan os…®mt…®zim bang…®n aremegham.
