\v 10 \x - \xo 20:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:14; Ofa Gami 18:20; God…®n Araziba 5:18\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam uan namakam…®n amuim ko dakuight…®, kamagh…®n ia gumazir kam ko amizir kam m…®sueght…® aning aremegh.
\v 11 \x - \xo 20:11 \xt Ofa Gami 18:8; God…®n Araziba 22:30; 27:20\x*Eght…® gumazim uan afeziam…®n amuim ko dakuigh, egh an arazir kuram…®n uan afeziam damuva aghums…®zim a dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, ia gumazir kam ko amizir kam m…®sueght…®, aning aremegh. Aning uaning arazir kuram damigh os…®mt…®zim ikiam, egh bizir kam bagh aning aremegham.
