\v 13 \x - \xo 20:13 \xt Ofa Gami 18:22\x*Eght…® gumazitam gumazir igharazim ko dakuigh, mati gumazim amizim ko akui mogh…®n, egh aning amizir arazir bar kurar k…® aghuazim damigh, bar os…®mt…®zir ekiam ikiam. Kamagh…®n ia aning m…®sueght…® aning aremegh. Aning uan os…®mt…®zim bang…®n aning aremegham.
\v 14 \x - \xo 20:14 \xt Ofa Gami 18:17; God…®n Araziba 27:23\x*Eght…® gumazitam uan amuim…®n ik…®, egh uaghan an amuim…®n amebam isafuragh uaghara aning…®n ik…®t…®, ia bar me is…® avim…®n me daboroght…® me isigh. Me os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam gami. Guizbang…®ra, kamagh…®n amir gumazamiziba ateght…®, me ian tong…®n ikian mark…®.
\v 15 \x - \xo 20:15-16 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:19; Ofa Gami 18:23; God…®n Araziba 27:21\x*Eght…® gumazitam as…®zitam ko arazir kuram damigham, mati gumazim amizim koma akui mogh…®n, eght…® ia uaghara aning m…®sueght…® aning aremegh.
\v 16 Eght…® amizitam as…®zitam bagh mang…®, a ko arazir kuram damigham, mati amizim gumazim koma akui mogh…®n, eght…® ia aning m…®sueght…® aning aremegh. Aning uan os…®mt…®zim bang…®n aning aremegham.
