\v 17 \x - \xo 20:17 \xt Ofa Gami 18:9; God…®n Araziba 27:22\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam uan buaramizim ko dakuam, kar an afeziam…®n guivim, o an amebam…®n guivim, egh aning bibiamra ik…® uaning…®n gan…®va, kamagh…®n aning arazir bar kuram damigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia gumazamizibar damazim…®n bar aning…®n atar…®va, aning batueght…®, aning ua ia ko ikian kogham. Gumazir kam uab…® uan buaramizim koma akui, kar aghums…®zir arazim, kamagh…®n, a uan arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim ateram.
