\v 19 \x - \xo 20:19-20 \xt Ofa Gami 18:12-14\x*‚ÄúGumazitam uan amebar dozim o afeziam…®n buaramizim ko dakuva, an arazir kuram…®n uan anabam damigh aghums…®zim a dan…®ngam. Aning amizir arazir kurar kam bang…®n os…®mt…®zim ateram.
\v 20 Eght…® gumazitam uan afeziar dozim…®n amuim ko dakuigham, gumazir kam aghums…®zim afeziar dozim dan…®ngam. Egh aning amizir arazir kurar kam…®n os…®mt…®zim ateram. Gumazir kam amizitam…®n ik…® boriba batan kogham, eght…® an afeziar dozim…®n amuim uaghan boriba batan kogham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 20:21 \xt Ofa Gami 18:16\x*Eght…® gumazitam uan aveghbuam…®n amuim a dam a inigh an ik…®, a nan damazim…®n arazir bar m…®z…®r…®zim damuva aghums…®zim uan aveghbuam dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir kam ko amizir kam boriba batan kogham.
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄúIa nan arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, bar dar g…®n mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, nguazir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian akua zuir kam, a ian aghuagh ia batueghan kogham, mati gumazim dagher kuram…®n mizi mok…®n. Ia deraghv…®ram an ikiam.
\v 23 Ia Kenan…®n nguazim…®n itir ik…®zibar arazibar g…®n mangan mark…®. Me bizir kurar kabagh ami, ez…® k…® bar men aghua. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ik…®zir kaba batueght…®, ia men nguazim iniam.
\v 24 K…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa, nguazir kam a bar dera, ez…® dagher av…®rim an ikia, deraghav…®ram aghui. K…® a is…® ia dan…®ngight…®, a ian nguazimram otogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ik…®zir igharazibar tong…®n ia ini, eght…® ia bar igharaghv…®ra ik…®, nan gumazamizibaram otogham.
\v 25 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia deraghv…®ra as…®ziba ko kuaraziba tuis…®gh, as…®ziba ko kuarazir manaba zue, ia dar am…®. Ez…® as…®ziba ko kuarazir manaba m…®zeght…®, ia dar aman mark…®. K…® as…®ziba ko kuaraziba ko apizir zuezir puvat…®zir kabar gun ia m…®keme. Ia dar am…®va, ia arazir bar kurir k…® aghuazibar amuam. Ia as…®zir kabar am…®va nan damazim…®n bar m…®zegham.
\v 26 Ia arazir kuraba ategh zuegh ik…®, nan arazir bar aghuibar g…®n mang…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® bar zue, egha k…® ik…®zir igharazibar tong…®n ua baghav…®ra ia ini.
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄúEght…® kukunir gumaziba, ko ariaghirezir gumazamizibar duaba ko m…®geiba, ia bar dag…®aba is…® me ginivight…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh. Me uan os…®mt…®zim bang…®n ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\c 21
\s1 Ofa gamir gumaziba God ifongezir arazir aghuibar g…®n mang…®
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumazibav k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\p ‚ÄúIan adarazir tav aremeght…®, ia gumazir aremezim bagh aghuimazir arazim damuan mark…®. Arazir kam ia gamima, ia nan damazim…®n m…®ze.
\v 2 Eght…® bar gumazim…®n adarazir aven iti tav aremegham, kar an amebam, o afeziam, o otarim, o guivim, o aveghbuam,
\v 3 o guiz…®n an buaramizir pam puvat…®gha afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n ikia aremezim, a me bagh aghuimazir arazim damuam. A kamagh…®n fogh, an aghuimazir arazir kam damut…®, a nan damazim…®n m…®zegham.
\v 4 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n ivozim aremegham, eght…® ofa gamir gumazim an aghuimazir arazim damuan mark…®. Kamagh…®n a nan damazim…®n m…®zegham.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 21:5 \xt Ofa Gami 19:27-28; God…®n Araziba 14:1\x*‚ÄúEght…® ia ofa gamir gumaziba, aghuimazir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®va, uan dapanir ar…®zir akuatabagh isan mark…®. Egh ghuamas…®zibar m…®riabagh isan mark…®. Egh aghuimazir arazim bagh tintinibar uan m…®karzibar ghoran mark…®.
\v 6 Ia ofa gamir gumaziba k…® ua bagha ia m…®sefe. K…® ian God, kamagh…®n ia nan ziam d…®kab…®nan mark…®. Ia nan ofa damuamin ingangarim iti, ez…® avim isir ofan kaba, ia daghebar m…®n na gan…®di. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia arazir kurar kaba ak…®rim ragh dagh asaragh, egh na ko daru.
\v 7 Ia nan ofa gamir gumazibara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tuavim…®n amizir gumaziba isava akuim, o amizir gumazir igharazim ko akuim, o amizir an pam anetaghizim, ia an poghan mark…®.
\v 8 Gumazamiziba fogh suam, ia ofabar dagheba na gan…®di, kamagh…®n, ia bar nan ofa gamir gumazibara. K…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. K…® God…®n bar zuegha arazir aghuibaram amim. Egha k…® uan gumazamizibagh amima, me zuegha arazir aghuibaram ami.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúEght…® ia ofa gamir gumazitam…®n guivitam, tuavim…®n amizim…®n ik…®va, arazir m…®z…®r…®zibar g…®n mang…®va, aghums…®zir ekiam uan afeziam dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, gumazamiziba avim…®n a daboroght…® a isigh aremegh.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúOfa gamir gumazibar dapanim, uan ingangarim…®n ziar ekiam ini. Me borem an dapanim gingezir dughiam…®n, me ofa gamir gumazibar korotiamra, a daghuasa anem…®sefe. Eght…® an adarazir tav aremeght…®, a uan dapanir ar…®zim ateght…® a pura ikian mark…®, a deraghv…®ram a batogh. Egh a uan korotiam ab…®ghan mark…®.
\v 11 Ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, gumazim…®n kuam itir danganim…®n borogh…®n mangan mark…®. A kamagh…®n damuva, nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. An afeziam o amebam aremeght…®, an aghuimazir dughiam…®n uab…® damu m…®zeghan mark…®.
\v 12 Kamagh…®n, an Anogoroghezir Danganim ategh gumazir kuaba itir danganim…®n borogh…®n mangan mark…®. A kamagh…®n damu nan Purirpenim damut…® a nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Ia borer k…® ia gan…®ngizir kam a gingegha g…®vagha, anem…®sevez…® a ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n oto. Kamagh…®n, a gumazim…®n kuam itir danganim…®n borogh…®n mangan mark…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®kemegha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúOfa gamir gumazibar dapanim, amizir gumazir igharazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zir tam…®n ik…®.
\v 14 An amizir pam aremezim, o amizir pam taghizim…®n ikian mark…®. A tuavim…®n amizir gumaziba isava akuim, o amizir gumazir igharazim arazir kuram…®n a gamua a ko akuizim…®n ikian mark…®. Kar amizir anogorogheziba. An ofa gamir gumazibar anabam…®n amizir gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zir tamra ik…®.
\v 15 Egh a nan akar kam…®n g…®n mangan koght…®, an boriba nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ua baghv…®ra anem…®sevegha, a isa ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n ingangarir kam damuasa anet…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\v 17 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Aron m…®kemegh: N…®n adarazir gumazitam dat…®r…®gh…®n o g…®n izamin dughiam…®n otoght…®, an m…®karzim duatam ik…® ikuvight…®, gumazir kam na bagh daghebar ofabar amuan mark…®.
\v 18 Gumazir m…®karziba ikuviziba, me nan borogh…®n iz…® na bagh ofabar amuan mark…®. K…® gumazir kamagh garibav gei: damazir okaviziba, o suer kuraba, o guar kuraba, o amebam…®n navim…®n averara sueba ko aghariba otevegha ik…®z…®r…®ghiziba,
\v 19 o gumazir suer kuraba, o gumazir agharir kuraba,
\v 20 o gumazir ak…®rir f…®ght…®ziba, o gumazir bar oteviba, o gumazir damazir kuraba, o gumazir m…®karzir kuraba, o gumazir turiaba ikuviziba.
\v 21 Guizbang…®ra, n…®n anabam…®n tav…®n m…®karzim duatam ikia ikufi, gumazir kam, na bagh iz…® daghebar ofabar amuan mark…®. K…® bar anogoroke.
\v 22 Egh an as…®ziba ko bizir ia ofan m…®n na gan…®ngizibar amam. K…® ofa gamir gumaziba damasa ia gan…®ngizir ofaba, a bar da iniam.
\v 23 Egh a Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim modir nir ekiam iti nagh…®n ko ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n mangan mark…®. K…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uan ingangarimra damuasa me am…®sefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an adar borogh…®n iz…®, egh a bizir bar zuezir kabar amut…® da nan damazim…®n m…®zegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Moses akar kam…®n gun Aron uan otariba, ko Israelian gumazamiziba bar me m…®keme.
\c 22
\s1 Ofaba, da God…®n bizibara
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Aron uan otariba ko me m…®k…®m. Ia deraghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, Israelian gumazamizibar ofaba, da nan bizibara. Kamagh amiz…®, ia deraghv…®ra ofan kabar gan. Puvat…®ght…®, ia nan ziar ekiam d…®kab…®ragham. K…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.
\v 3 N…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m. Ia ofa gamir gumaziba, ian adarazir tav nan damazim…®n m…®zegh, a Israelia na gan…®dir ofabar borogh…®n izan mark…®. Egh a rogh…®ra mang…®t…®, k…® uan damazim…®n a batueght…® an ofa gamir gumazim…®n ingangarim damuan kogham. Ia zurara arazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®v…®ra ik…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 4-5 ‚ÄúEght…® Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumazitam, lepan ar…®mariam ik…®, o m…®karzir mogomem duam a batoght…® ghuzir m…®t…®zim an azenan otivt…®, ghuzir m…®t…®zir kam a damut…®, a nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. Egh a nan ofabar aman kogh mang…®, a ua deraghamin dughiam…®n tugham. Egh a uaghan gumazir aremezim…®n kuam…®n poroghav itir bizitam…®n suiragham, o d…®pam an m…®karzir mogomem…®n otivam, o a dafarir tam…®n as…®zir m…®zezir tam…®n suiragham, a gumazir nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®zim, ez…® arazir kam bang…®n, an ofabar aman kogham.
\v 6 Ofa gamir gumazir nan damazim…®n m…®zezir manam, a kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® aruem mag…®r…®gham. Egh a faragh d…®pam…®n deragh uab…® ruegh, egh a ofan as…®zir me na gan…®dibar amam. Egh a rueghan kogh, a daman kogham.
\v 7 Aruem mag…®r…® g…®vaght…®, a ua zuegh nan ofabar amam. K…® uab…®, uan ofabar dagheba isa ia bagha da at…®, kar ofa gamir gumazibar dagheba.
\v 8 A puram aremezir as…®zim ko as…®zir atiam m…®soghez…® aremezim…®n tuzitam aman mark…®. Ana anemegham, a nan damazim…®n m…®zegham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.
\v 9 Ia ofa gamir gumaziba, Akar Gavgavir k…® ia gan…®ngiziba bar adar g…®n mang…®. Ia nan akam batuegh, ia arazir kuram damigh, os…®mt…®zim ik…®t…®, k…® ia m…®sueght…® ia ar…®ghiregham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ua bagha ia ofa gamir gumaziba am…®sefe, egha k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúOfa gamir gumazibar adarazir gumazim o amizim, merara gumazamiziba na gan…®dir ofabar amam. Igharazitav daman kogham. Gumazir dughiar otevim…®n ofa gamir gumazim ko itim, o an ingangarir gumazim, me uaghan daman kogham. Bar markiam.
\v 11 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nir a ivezeziba, ko borir amebam ofa gamir gumazir kam…®n d…®penim…®n ikia oteziba, me ofa gamir gumaziba apir daghebar am…®.
\v 12 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazitam…®n guivim, ofa gamir gumazibar ik…®zim…®n azenan itir gumazir k…®nitam ko porogh…®v ik…®, kamagh…®n a nan ofabar aman mark…®.
\v 13 Eght…® guivir kam…®n pam aremeght…® a pura ikiam, o an pam aneteght…®, a pura ik…®va, boriba puvat…®gh, uamategh uan afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n mang…®, kamagh…®n, an ofa gamir gumazibar daghebar am…®, kar dagher an afeziam inigh izamiba. Eght…® gumazim o amizim ofa gamir gumazibar adarazir aven itir puvat…®, a daman mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúEgh gumazitam ofa gamir gumazibar adarazir mav puvat…®, egh deragh n…®ghnighan kogh nan ofan nataba amegh, kamagh…®n a dagher kaba ikarvagh ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngigh. A 5plan dagher naba inigh, kamagh…®n a 6plan dagheba is…® da ikarvagham.
\v 15 Ia ofa gamir gumaziba deraghv…®ra gan, gumazamizir k…®niba nan ofan kabar aman bar mark…®.
\v 16 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ua bagha ofan kaba m…®sefe, egha dar anogoroke. Kamagh amiz…®, ia ofa gamir gumaziba, gumazir k…®nitam…®n amamangat…®ght…® a ofan kabar aman bar mark…®. Gumazir kaba dar am…®va, os…®mt…®zim ikiam, egh ua dagheba ikarvagh da is…® ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme,
\v 18 ‚ÄúN…® akar kam is…® Aron uan otariba ko Israelian gumazamizibav m…®kemegh. Ia Israelian gumazitam, o ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir Israel…®n kantrin ititam, an as…®zir tam is…® ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim bagh an aku izam, kar ofan a uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim na ko amizim ak…®rasa, o a uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua ofa damuasa,
\v 19 a bulmakaun apurim o sipsip…®n apuritam o memen apurir tam inigh iz…®. Ia duaba m…®karzim…®n itir as…®zitam…®n ofa damuan mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® a gifueghan kogham.
\v 20 \x - \xo 22:20 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:1\x*Ia deraghv…®ram oragh. Ia as…®zir m…®karzim ikuviz…® tam…®n ofa damut…®, k…® a gifueghan kogham.
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúGumazim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofa damuam, kar ofan a uan akar d…®k…®r…®zir na ko amizim ak…®rasa, o a uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…® ofa damuasa, a bulmakau o sipsip…®n duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®zitam inigh iz…®. A kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® an ofa gifuegham.
\v 22 Ia as…®zir damazir okav…®r…®ziba, o as…®zir suer kuraba itiba, o as…®zir m…®karzim ikuviziba, o as…®zir duar ekiaba itiba, o as…®zir tuar k…®niba, o as…®zir duar kuriba itiba is…®, nan ofa damuan mark…®. Ia as…®zir katam nan ofa gamir dakozim…®n avim…®n an ofa damuan mark…®.
\v 23 Egh ia uari ofan tam uan ifongiam…®n a damus…®, bulmakau o sipsip…®n soroghafariba otevezitam o ik…®z…®r…®zir tam iniam, a dera. Egh ia akar na ko d…®k…®r…®zir tam ak…®rs…®, as…®zir katam is…® nan ofa damuan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\v 24 Eght…® as…®zir katam…®n turiam ikufi, o me an oke, o aneb…®ki, o me an turiar ov…®zim am…®sefe, as…®zir kam ia na bagh ofa damuan mark…®. Ia as…®zir kamagh…®n gariba, uan nguazim…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damuan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\v 25 Egh ia ik…®zir igharazim…®n gumazim…®n dafarim…®n as…®zir katam inigh ofa damuan mark…®. As…®zir kamagh gariba, dar m…®karziba ikuvigha, nan damazim…®n derazir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® ofan kamagh…®n garibar aghua. K…® bar dar aghua.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\v 27 ‚ÄúBulmakau ko sipsip ko memeba otamin dughiam…®n, dar nguziba 7plan aruebar amebam ko ikegham. Eght…® namba 8…®n aruem…®n ikegh mang…®, ia da inigh avim…®n ofa damus…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, eght…® k…® ian ofa gifuegham.
\v 28 Eght…® ia bulmakaun amebam, o sipsip…®n amebam, o memen amebam, uan nguzim ko, ia aruer vam…®ra uaghara aning m…®suegh aning…®n ofa damuan mark…®. Bar mark…®.
\v 29 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia na m…®nabir ofan tam damus…®, ia ofan arazibar g…®n mang…®t…®, k…® ian ofa gifuegham.
\v 30 Ia aruer manam…®n ofa gami, ia aruer kamra ofan as…®zir tuzibar amegh. Ia da ateght…® da ik…® mang…® am…®mzaraghan otoghan mark…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®kemegha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 31 ‚ÄúIa oragh. Ia deraghv…®ra nan Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mang…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.
\v 32 \x - \xo 22:32-33 \xt Ofa Gami 11:45\x*Ia nan ziar bar zuezim d…®kab…®nan mark…®. Ia Israelian gumazamiziba kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® God…®n bar zuezimra. K…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ua bagha ia m…®sevez…®, ia bar nan gumazamizir aghuibaram otifi.
\v 33 K…® ian God…®n ikiasa, kamagh…®n, k…® fom…®ra Isip…®n kantrin aven, ia isa ian akua azenan ize. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n ami.‚Äù
\c 23
\s1 God…®n ziam fer dughiar ekiaba
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav m…®kemegh: Kar dughiar ekiar ia nan ziam fasa k…® inabaziba. Ia uari akuvagh dughiar kabar nan ziam fam.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:8-10; 23:12; 31:15; 34:21; 35:2; God…®n Araziba 5:12-14\x*‚ÄúIa 6plan aruebar ingangaribar amu. Egh aruer namba 7, kar Sabat…®n dughiam, avughsazir dughiar kam…®n ia ingaran mark…®. Ia uari akuvagh nan ziam f…®. Egh ia danganir manam…®n iti, ia na bagh Sabat…®n dughiam am…®sefegh, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.
\v 4 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia bagha m…®sevezir dughiabar gun ia m…®k…®masa. Egh azenibar zurara ia dughiar kabar uari akuv nan ziam f…®.‚Äù
\s1 God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam, ko Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam
\r (D…®boboniba 28:16-25)
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 23:5 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:1-13; God…®n Araziba 16:1-2\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúIa, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuam. Dughiar kam, azeniba vaghvagha, dar iak…®nir faragha zuim, an namba 14…®n aruem…®n guarat…®zim…®n, ia uari akuvagh nan ziam f…®.
\v 6 \x - \xo 23:6-8 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:14-20; 23:15; 34:18; God…®n Araziba 16:3-8\x*Ez…® iak…®nir kam…®n namba 15…®n aruem…®n, kar Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam. Egh ia yis puvat…®zir bret…®n kam am…® mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh.
\v 7 Eght…® aruer kabar faragha zuir aruem…®n, ia uari akuvagh nan ziam f…®va, uan ingangaribar amuan mark…®.
\v 8 Ia as…®ziba ko dagheba is…® avim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damu mang…® 7plan aruebar tugh. Egh namba 7 aruem…®n ia ua uari akuvagh nan ziam f…®. Dughiar kam…®n, ia uan ingangaribar amuan mark…®.‚Äù
\s1 Dagher faragha anigha g…®vazibar ofaba
\p 
\v 9 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 10 ‚ÄúN…® Israelian gumazamiziba kamagh…®n me m…®kemegh: Dughiar ia mang…® nguazir k…® ia dan…®ngamim…®n ikiamim…®n, ia wit…®n ian azenibar itir aniziba inigh, egh zurara azeniba bar, wit…®n ik…®zir ia faragha ikeziba, ia da ater ofa gamir gumaziba bagh mang…®.
\v 11 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim wit…®n ik…®zir kam…®n suiragh a fegh a damut…®, a nan damazim…®n ighuavamang, eght…® k…® ia gifuegham. Ofa gamir gumazim, Sabat…®n g…®n otivamin aruem…®n, an ofan kam damu.
\v 12 Eght…® ia wit…®n ofabar amuamin dughiam…®n, ia sipsip…®n nguzir azenir vam…®ra itim…®n ofa damu, a bar deragh duaba an m…®karzim…®n puvat…®gham. Eght…® sipsip…®n kam, an ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim.
\v 13 Egh ia plauan nar aghuim inigh, an os…®mt…®zim 2 kilogrem, egh oliv…®n borem ko a veregh wit…®n ofa tu. Ia ofan isia bar m…®gh…®rim sara an ofa damu, eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ofan tuamin kam…®n mughuriar aghuim baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam. Egh uaghan, ia 1 lita wain…®n d…®pam inigh ofan kamning sara ofa damu.
\v 14 Ia wit…®n ik…®zir faragha ikezir kam, ia uan God bagh a inigh izeghan kogh…®va, ia wit…®n igiar faragha azenim…®n inizir kam aman mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia faragh wit…®n ik…®zir faragha ikezir kam inigh izegh, egh g…®n ia wit…®n igiam am…®. Ia wit…®n ov…®zir isizir puvat…®ziba, ko wit…®n ov…®zir ia avim…®n tuamiba, ko bret…®n ia ingarigh tuamiba, ia dar am…®. Ia ofan arazir k…® ifongezir kam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, ian ovavir g…®n otivamiba, me uaghan dar g…®n mangam.‚Äù
\s1 Azenibar Dagher Igiaba Asiamin Dughiam…®n Isar Ekiam
\r (D…®boboniba 28:26-31)
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 23:15-21 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:16; 34:22; God…®n Araziba 16:9-12\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa na bagha wit…®n ik…®ziba atera izir aruem…®n g…®n, 7plan wighba mengegh.
\v 16 Egh namba 7 wigh g…®vaght…®, aruer namba 50 otoght…®, ia ua wit…®n igiam…®n ofan igharazim na dan…®ng.\f + \fr 23:16 \ft Israelian dughiar ekiar kam, me Grigh…®n akam…®n me, ‚ÄúPentekos,‚Äù a gar…®si. Ez…® Grigh…®n akam…®n aven ziar kam, a ‚Äú50plan arueba,‚Äù an m…®rara ghu. N…® uaghan Aposel 2:1…®n gan.\f*
\v 17 Ian avitoriba vaghvagh bret…®n rubuzir pumuning inigh iz…® na dan…®ngigh, kar wit…®n faragha anibar ofa. Ia bret…®n rubuzimning…®n ingars…® bret…®n rubuzir tam bagh, plauan aghuir 2 kilogrem…®n itim inigh…®va, yis koma a veregh, egh bret…®n rubuzir igharazim uaghan kamagh…®ra an ingarigh, aning tuagh. Egh bret…®n rubuzir kamning inigh iz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damu. Ia aning…®n suiragh aning f…® aning damut…®, aning Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ighuavamang.
\v 18 Ia bizir kaba sara bret…®n kam…®n ofa damu. Ia 7plan sipsip…®n nguzir azenir vam…®ra itiba, ko bulmakaun apurir igiar tam, ko sipsip…®n apurir pumuning inigh iz…®. Ia as…®zir duaba m…®karzibar itiba inian mark…®. As…®zir aghuibara inigh. Egh ia ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim na bagh a damu. Egh ia zuraram ami mogh…®n, wit…®n taba ko wain sara, ofan kam dat…®gh. Ofan kam avim an isi mang…® a bar m…®gh…®right…®, averenir k…®nim…®n otogh. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ofan kam…®n mughuriar aghuim baregh, a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.
\v 19 Ia memen apuritam inigh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damu, egh sipsip…®n apurir igiar azenir vam…®ra itir pumuning inigh, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa damu.
\v 20 Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim wit…®n faragha anibar ofan m…®n, bret…®n kam ko sipsip…®n nguzimning…®n suiragh da f…® da dar amut…®, da nan damazim…®n ighuavamang…®. Bizir kaba nan bizibara. Eght…® k…® da inigh ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngam.
\v 21 Ia ofan kam gamir dughiam…®n ia uari akuvagh, nan ziar ekiam f…®, egh ia uan ingangaribar amuan mark…®. Ian ovaviba g…®n otivigh managh ik…®, me bar zurara arazir kam…®n g…®n mangam.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 23:22 \xt Ofa Gami 19:9-10; God…®n Araziba 24:19-22\x*‚ÄúDughiar ia uan azeniba aghorim…®n, ia dagher azenim…®n dazighiam…®n tughav itim asian mark…®. Egh ia azenibar tong…®n dagheba asi, egh taba ategh…®va, ua mang…® da asian mark…®. Ia da ateght…® da mamagh…®ra ik…®t…®, onganarazir gumazamiziba ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, me da iniam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù
\s1 S…®ghabagh Iviamin Dughiar Ekiam
\r (D…®boboniba 29:1-6)
\p 
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\v 24 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav kemegh. Namba 7…®n iak…®nim, an aruer faragha zuim…®n ia avughs…®. Kar ian dughiar ekiar mam, egh ia s…®ghabagh ivi uari akuv, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®nab…®va an ziam f…®.
\v 25 Dughiar kam…®n ia uan ingangaribar amuan mark…®. Ia ofa gamir dakozim…®n mang…®, egh avim…®n nan ofa damu.‚Äù
\s1 God Gumazamizibar Arazir Kuraba G…®n Amadir Dughiar Ekiam
\r (D…®boboniba 29:7-11)
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 23:26-32 \xt Ofa Gami 16:29-34\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei:
\v 27 ‚ÄúNamba 7…®n iak…®nim, an namba 10…®n aruem, kar Gumazamizibar Arazir Kuraba G…®n Amadir Dughiar Ekiam. Egh dughiar kam…®n ia dagheba ko agoroger araziba atakigh. Ia uari akuvagh nan ziam f…® na m…®nab…®va na bagh avim…®n tuamin ofan tam inigh iz…®.
\v 28 Aruer kam…®n, God Gumazamizibar Arazir Kuraba G…®n Amadir Dughiar Ekiam. Ofa gamir gumazim, ia bagh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damut…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® ian arazir kuraba bar da g…®n amadagham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia aruer kam…®n ingaran mark…®.
\v 29 Eght…® gumazitam aruer kam…®n daghebar am…®va uan agorogeba ab…®raghan koght…®, k…® uan gumazamizibar tong…®n a batuegham.
\v 30 Eght…® gumazitam ingangaritam aruer kam…®n a damut…®, k…® uab…® uan gumazamizibar tong…®n a m…®sueght…®, an aremegham.
\v 31 Ia oragh. K…® ua m…®gei, ia ingangaritam aruer kam…®n a damuan mark…®. Ia arazir k…® ifongezir kam zurara an g…®n mang…®. Eght…® ian ovavir g…®n otivigh managh ikiamiba, me uaghan an g…®n mang…®.
\v 32 Ia dughiar ekiar kam…®n deraghv…®ra avughs…®. Iak…®nir kam, an aruer namba 9…®n, aruem uaghirir dughiam…®n ikegh mang…®t…®, aruer namba 10…®n aruem ghuaghiri dughiam otoght…®, dughiar kam bar mogh…®ra, ia an dagheba ko agoroger biziba bar da atakigh.‚Äù
\s1 Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiaba
\r (D…®boboniba 29:12-40)
\p 
\v 33-34 \x - \xo 23:33-36 \xt God…®n Araziba 16:13-15\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar kam Israelia dan…®ngasa kamagh…®n Moses m…®keme: ‚ÄúIak…®nir namba 7, an aruer namba 15…®n, kar Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam. Dughiar kam…®n, gumazamiziba temer aguabar averpenibar ingaram, egh 7plan aruebar dar ik…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n…®ghn…®gh.
\v 35 Egh wigh…®n kam…®n faragha zuir aruem…®n, ia nan ziam f…®s…® uari akuv, egh ia uan ingangaribar amuan mark…®.
\v 36 Egh ia wigh…®n kam…®n arueba bar ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damuam. Egh namba 8…®n aruem…®n, ia ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n…®ghn…®gh an ziam f…®s…® uari akuv, egh an ofan avim…®n tuamiba inigh iz…® dar ofa damu. Aruer namba 8, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam famin dughiam, kamagh…®n amiz…® ia uan ingangaribar amuan mark…®.
\p 
\v 37 ‚ÄúAruer kaba, kar nan dughiar ekiabara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. Ia nan ziam f…®s…® uari akuv, avim…®n na bagh ofabar amu. Ia ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba, ko wit tuer ofa, ko wain ingamin ofa, ko ofan igharazir maba, ia ofan kaba vaghvagh dar aruebara dar amu.
\v 38 Ia dughiar ekiar kabar g…®n mang…®, egh uaghan nan Sabat…®n dughiabar g…®n mang…®. Egh uaghan bizir ia zurara na gan…®diba, ko akar d…®k…®r…®ziba ak…®ramin ofaba, ko ofan ia uari uan ifongiabar g…®n mang…® na dan…®ngamiba, ia bar da is…® na dan…®ngam.
\p 
\v 39 \x - \xo 23:39-43 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:16; 34:22\x*‚ÄúEz…® namba 7…®n iak…®nim…®n, an dughiar namba 15…®n, ia faragh dagher faragha aniziba inigh g…®vagh, egh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dughiar ekiar kam damuam, an aruer namba 15…®n ikegh, 7plan aruebar mangam. Dughiar kabar, ia averpenibar ik…®va na g…®n…®ghn…®gham. Dughiar ekiar kam…®n aruer faragha zuim ko namba 8 aruem…®n, ia bar avughs…®.
\v 40 Aruer faragha zuim…®n ia temer ov…®zir ia apibar dagher bar aghuitaba inigh. Ia temer det…®n aguaba ko temer dafarir av…®riba itibar aguaba inigh. Egh ia nan damazim…®n 7plan aruebar bar akongegh. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God.
\v 41 Egh azeniba bar dar namba 7…®n iak…®nim…®n, ia 7plan dughiar kaba na bagh da m…®sevegh, dughiar ekiar kam damuam. Ian ovaviba g…®n otivigh zurara arazir kabar g…®n mangam.
\v 42 Ia Israelian gumazamiziba bar, 7plan aruebar averpenir muziaribar ik…®.
\v 43 Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, ian ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba ganigh fogham, k…® Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha ian akua azenan ize, egha dughiar kam…®n k…® ia gamima, ia averpenir muziaribar iti. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 44 Moses akar kam baregha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam famin dughiar ekiar a inabazibar gun Israelian gumazamizibav gei.
\c 24
\s1 God…®n Purirpenim…®n lambar // garir arazim
\r (Ua Me Ini 27:20-21)
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei:
\v 2 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Israelia m…®kemegh. Me lam…®n nan Purirpenim…®n itiba bagh oliv…®n borer bar aghuim inigh iz…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumaziba d…®magaribar zurara lam…®n kabar apongt…® da isi mamagh…®ra ik…®.
\v 3 Lam…®n kaba, Aron guarat…®zibar dar apong, eght…® d…®magariba bar lamba isi mamagh…®ra ik…®t…® am…®nim tiragham. Lam…®n kaba, God bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven ik…® inir ekiar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam modozim…®n azenan tuivigh ik…® nan damazim…®n isiam.
\v 4 Lam…®n kaba, da aghorir me gol…®n aghuarim…®n ingarizim gis…®n ik…®t…®, Aron deragh dar gant…®, dar angazangariba mungeghan kogham, egh da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n is…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, k…® dar ganam.‚Äù
\s1 Bret…®n me isa God gan…®dim
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 24:5-6 \xt Ua Me Ini 25:30\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa 12 kilogrem plauan aghuiba iniva, 12plan bret…®n rubuzibar ingarigh. Ia vaghvagh bret…®n rubuzim…®n ingars…®, plauan os…®mt…®zir 1 kilogrem…®n itim inigh.
\v 6 Egh g…®n ia bret…®n kaba is…®, dakozir bar zuezir me gol…®n aghuarim…®n an pogha a noghezir kam…®n, pozir pumuning…®n dar ar…®kigh, eght…® 6pla vong…®n ik…®t…® 6pla vong…®n ik…®, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ikiam.
\v 7 Egh ia pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim is…® bret…®n pozir kamning…®n borogh…®n dar ar…®kigh, egh g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh avim…®n pauran kam…®n nan ofa damu, a bret…®n kabar danganim iniam.
\v 8 Egh Sabat…®n dughiabar zurara ofa gamir gumazim bret…®n kam dakozim dat…®ght…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ikiam. Israelia arazir kamra g…®n mang…®. Kar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir mam, k…® me koma a gami, eght…® a zurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
\v 9 \x - \xo 24:9 \xt Matyu 12:4; Mak 2:26; Luk 6:4\x*Kar dagher gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha avim…®n ofa gamiziba, da bar nan bizibara. Eght…® k…® da is…® Aron…®n ovavir boribar an…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, bret…®n kam dat…®r…®gh…®n ko g…®n izamin dughiabar, an Aron…®n adarazir bret, ez…® me bret…®n kam nan Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven anerem…®.‚Äù
\s1 God gumazir mam amizir arazir kuraba ikarvazir arazim m…®gei
\p 
\v 10-11 Dughiar mam, gumazir mam iti, an afeziam Isipian gumazim, an amebam Israelian amizim. Amebam…®n ziam Selomit, Selomit a Dibrin guivim, a Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazir mav. Egha Selomit…®n otarir kam, a me itir danganim…®n ikia, egha Israelian gumazir mam ko m…®sosi. Aning uaning m…®sogha ghua, Selomit…®n otarim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam d…®bora akar kuram m…®g…®a an ziam gas…®ghas…®zima, me a baraki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me a inigha Moses bagha ghu.
\v 12 Ez…® Moses a isa gumazir mabagh an…®ngiz…®, me kalabuz…®n m…®n a ikegha a geghuva ikia, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®zuai, a manmagh…®n gumazir kam m…®k…®mt…®, me arazir manatam…®n a damuam.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,
\v 14 ‚ÄúN…® gumazir kam inigh danganir ia itim…®n azenan mang…®. Eght…® gumazir a na m…®kemezir akar kuraba baraghiziba, me bar uan dafariba an dapanim dar…®kigh. Me kamagh…®n damight…®, gumazamiziba fogham, gumazir kam arazir kuram gamigha os…®mt…®zim iti. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar dag…®aba f…®va a m…®k…®nt…® an aremegham.
\v 15 Eght…® g…®n n…® Israelia m…®k…®m suam: Gumazitam akar kuram…®n na m…®kemegham, an arazir kuram gamigha g…®fa, egh a uan arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim ateram.
\v 16 Gumazitam akar kuratam m…®k…®m…®va Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam d…®ponam, kamagh…®n an aremegham. A Israelian gumazimra, o ik…®zir igharazim…®n gumazamizir ian tong…®n ititam, gumazir nan ziam gas…®ghas…®ghamin manatam, gumazamiziba bar uari akuvagh dag…®aba f…®va gumazir kam m…®k…®night…® an aremegh.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:12\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam gumazim o amizim m…®sueght…® an aremegham, eght…® ia uaghan a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 18 Eght…® gumazitam gumazir igharazim…®n bulmakaun m…®sueght…® an aremegham, a bulmakaun igharazitam…®n a ikaragh. Os…®mt…®zir kabanang ak…®ramin arazim a kamak…®n, gumazitam gumazir igharazim…®n as…®zim m…®soghez…® an areme, an as…®zir kamagh…®n garimra an as…®zim ikaragh.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam gumazir igharazim…®n m…®karzim gas…®ghasigham, eght…® ia arazir kamram a ikaragh.
\v 20 \x - \xo 24:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:23-25; God…®n Araziba 19:21; Matyu 5:38\x*A gumazir igharazim…®n agharim ap…®right…®, ia uaghan an agharim ap…®righ. A gumazir igharazim…®n damazim gas…®ghas…®ght…®, ia uaghan an damazim gas…®ghas…®kigh. A gumazir igharazim…®n atariba ap…®right…®, ia uaghan an atariba ap…®righ. Gumazir manam bizim gamua, gumazir igharazim gas…®ghas…®ki, eght…® ia arazir kamra uam a ikaragh.
\v 21 Gumazim gumazir igharazim…®n as…®zim m…®sueght…® an aremegham, eght…® an as…®zir kamagh garimra a ikaragh. Eght…® gumazitam gumazir igharazim m…®soght…® an aremegham, eght…® ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.
\v 22 \x - \xo 24:22 \xt D…®boboniba 15:16\x*K…® Israelia ia ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba sara ia bagha Arazir kam at…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian God, k…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Moses akar kabar gun Israelia m…®kemegha g…®fa. Ez…® g…®n me gumazir akar kuram…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®kemezir kam inigha danganir me itim…®n azenan ghu. Egha me dag…®abar a giniviz…® an areme. Ez…® arazir kam…®n, Israelia Akar Gavgavir Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses gan…®ngizim…®n g…®n zui.
\c 25
\s1 Azenir namba 7…®n Araziba
\r (God…®n Araziba 15:1-11)
\p 
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 25:1-7 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:10-11\x*Moses Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar kam Israelia m…®k…®masa a gan…®ngi: ‚ÄúIa g…®n nguazir k…® ia dan…®ngasa m…®kemezir kam…®n mang…® an otivigh, egh zurara namba 7…®n azenim…®n, ia nguazir kam…®n dagheba oparan mark…®. Ia nguazim ateght…®, a pura ik…®. Ia Sabat…®n dughiabar avughsi mogh…®n, nguazim uaghan avughsam. Ia kamagh…®n damuva m…®k…®m suam, namba 7…®n azenim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azenimra, kamagh…®n nguazim avughsi.
\v 3 Ia 6plan azenibar, dagheba uan nguazim…®n da opar, egh wain…®n ikar…®zibar agharibar ghor…®va azenibar dagheba iniam.
\v 4 Egh ia namba 7…®n azenim…®n, ia nguazim ateght…®, an avughs…®. Egh ia azenir kam na bagh a anem…®seveght…® a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Sabat…®n azenim…®n ikiam. Kamagh amiz…®, ia azenir kam…®n dagheba oparan mark…®, egh ia uan wain…®n ikar…®zibar aghariba aghoran mark…®.
\v 5 Eght…® wit…®n taba puram otivigham, ia dar ov…®ziba inigh…®va dagher d…®penim…®n dar ar…®ghan mark…®. Egh wain…®n ov…®ziba pura dar agharibar otivight…®, ia da inigh wain…®n ingaran mark…®. Bar markiam. Azenir kam…®n nguazim deraghv…®ram avughsam, kamagh…®n, ia aneteght…® a pura ik…®.
\v 6 Eght…® azenir kam…®n dagheba pura ian nguazim…®n otivt…®, ia dar am…®. Ia da is…® dagher d…®penim…®n dar ar…®ghan mark…®, egh wainbar amuan mark…®. Ia ko, ingangarir gumazir k…®niba ko ingangarir amizir k…®niba, ko ingangarir gumazir igharaziba, ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba, ia bar dar am…®.
\v 7 Egh bulmakauba, sipsipba, memeba, ko as…®zir atiaba sara ia dar am…®.‚Äù
\s1 Azenir ua biziba ikarvaghamim
\p 
\v 8 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa 7plan dughiabar, 7plan azeniba meng mang…®, kamagh…®ra damu mang…® 49plan azenibar otogh.
\v 9 Egh ia azenir 49…®n, an namba 7…®n iak…®nim, an dughiar namba 10…®n, ia gumazitaba ameght…® me ian nguibaba bar dar mang…® s…®ghabagh ivi. Kar Dughiar Ekiar Gumazamizibar Arazir Kuraba G…®n Amadim.
\v 10 Namba 50…®n azenim…®n ia dat…®r…®gh…®n s…®ghabagh iviamin dughiam…®n ikegh mang…® azenir vam…®ran tugham, ia a damut…®, a nan azenimra ik…®. Eght…® ia gumazamizibav m…®k…®m suam, me azenir kam…®n f…®righ…®reght…® men os…®mt…®ziba g…®vaght…® me deraghv…®ra ikiam. Azenir kam…®n, gumazir gumazir igharazibar nguazibagh ivezeziba, me vaghvagh ua nguazir kaba is…® dar guiz…®n ghuavibar an…®ngigh, o men adarazir an…®ngigh. Eght…® ingangarir gumazamizir k…®niba, me vaghvagh ingangarir kam ategh, ua uan adarazi baghv…®ra mang…®.
\v 11 Guizbang…®ra, namba 50…®n azenim…®n, gumazamiziba deraghv…®ra dapiagh avughs…® bar akuegham. Egh azenir kam…®n ia uan nguazibar dagheba oparan mark…®, egh ia wit…®n puram otivibar ghor da akuvan mark…®. Egh ia wain…®n d…®pabar ingars…®, wain…®n ov…®ziba inian mark…®.
\v 12 Azenir kam, ia deraghv…®ra dapiagh avughs…® bar akongegh bar a g…®n…®ghn…®gh, kar bar nan azenimra. Egh ia pura nguazim…®n otivir daghebara dam…®. Ia dagher igharazibar aman mark…®.
\p 
\v 13 ‚ÄúEght…® azenir kam…®n gumazir nguaziba isa igharaz darazir da amangiziba, ia ua me dama uan nguaziba iniam.
\v 14-15 Kamagh…®n, ia nguazim isa gumazir igharazim…®n amadaz…®, o a da nguazim givese, egh ia uarigh ifaran kogham. Ia n…®ghn…®gh, azeniba manmagh…®n ikiav…®ra iti, eght…® bar akongamin azenim otoght…® ia ua bizir kaba ikarvagham, egh manmagh…®n dughiabar an opar…®va dagheba iniam. Ia bar deraghv…®ra nguazir kam…®n dagheba iniamin azenir ikiav…®ra itibar ivezim givesegh.
\v 16 Eght…® azenir av…®riba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, dar nguazim…®n ivezim mavanang. Eght…® azenibar d…®bobonim oteveght…®, nguazim…®n ivezim mag…®r…®. Guizbang…®ra, a guiz…®n nguazim givezezir pu. Puvat…®, a nguazir kam…®n otivir daghebagh ivese. A nguazir an agharim…®n ikiav…®ra itir kam…®n azeniba meng…®va, an azenir kabar nguazir kam…®n otivir daghebagh ivezam.
\v 17 Ia uari uan namakatam gifaran bar mark…®. Ia uan God…®n atiating, egh arazir aghuibara damu. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù
\s1 God gumazamizir an akam…®n g…®n zuiba deraghv…®ra me damuam
\p 
\v 18 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemezibar suiragh dar g…®n mang…®, egh ia deraghv…®ra nguazir k…® ia dan…®ngamin kam…®n ikiam.
\v 19 Eght…® dagher av…®rim nguazim…®n otivt…®, ia zurara dagher av…®ribar am…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Egh ia bar deraghv…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikiam.
\v 20 Egh ia ua kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòNamba 7…®n azenim…®n e dagheba oparan kogham, egh dagher aniziba inigh da akuvan kogham. Egh e kamagh…®n damuan kogh, e azenir kam…®n tizim amam?‚Äô
\v 21 Mark…®, ia m…®gh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® namba 6…®n azenim…®n bar deragh nguazim damight…®, dagher av…®riba otivt…®ma ia dam…® mang…® 3plan azenibar tugham.
\v 22 Egh ia namba 8…®n azenim…®n dagheba opar, egh ia namba 6…®n azenibar inizir daghebar am…®v…®ra ikiam. Egh ia dagheba ik…®v…®ra ik…® mang…®, ia dagher igiaba iniamin dughiam otogham.‚Äù
\s1 Nguazir me iniziba, me ua da ikarvagham
\p 
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir igharazitam ia da nguazim givezegh, dughiar ruarim…®n an suighan mark…®. Kar guizbang…®ra ian nguazim puvat…®. Kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n nguazim, ez…® k…® Israelia ian taghiz…® ia an iti, mati gumazamiziba nguibar igharaziba ataghiz…® me men nguazibar iti.
\p 
\v 24 ‚ÄúEght…® ian gumazitam, ian namakar igharazitam da nguazim gives…®, a deraghv…®ra fogh, eght…® g…®n nguazir kam…®n guiz…®n ghuavim ua nguazim gives…®, a givezam.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúEght…® ian gumazitam bar biziba puvat…®gh, dag…®aba bagh gumazir igharazim ateght…®, an an nguazim givezeght…®, an anabar gumazim an akuragh a gives…® pura ik…®, egh nguazir kam uam a givezegh uam a dan…®ngigh.\f + \fr 25:25 \ft Hibrun arazim, gumazitam os…®mt…®zim batogham, eght…® an anabatam an gan…®va egh akurvaghamin ingangarim iti. Bizir bar ekiar namakar kam damuamim, an os…®mt…®zim itir gumazim…®n nguazim givezam, eght…® nguazir kam an adarazir nguazimra. N…® Rut 3:9-13 ko 4:1-6, ko Jeremaia 32:6-12…®n gan. Asaian Ak…®nafarim…®n akar is…®n zuir mam ghaze, God a gumazir gumazamizibar gan…®va egh men akurvaghamin ingangarim itim. N…® uaghan, Aisaia 41:14 ko 43:14 ko 44:6 ko 44:24 ko 54:5 ko 60:16…®n gan.\f*
\v 26 Eght…® gumazir kam…®n akuragh uam a givezamin anabam…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®ght…®, a uab…® g…®n dag…®ar av…®riba itir dughiam, a ua nguazir kam givezam.
\v 27 A biziba ua da ikarvaghamin azenim g…®foghs…®, an azeniba meng, da manmagh…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Egh an azenir kam…®n dagher nguazir kam…®n otivamiba bar dar ivezim…®n d…®bobonim manmagh…®n otogham. Egh a dag…®aba inigh dagher kaba bagh, gumazir fom…®ram an nguazim givezezim a danigh, ua nguazir kam iniam.
\v 28 Egh an dag…®aba oteveght…®, a nguazir kam uam a givezeghan kogham, kamagh…®n gumazir fom…®ram an nguazim givezezim, nguazim an dafarim…®n ik…® mang…®t…® azenir ua biziba ikarvaghamim otogham. Eght…® azenir kam otoghamin dughiam…®n, gumazir nguazir kam givezezim, a ua nguazir kam is…® an ghuavimra dan…®ngigh.
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven uan d…®penim anemadaz…®, gumazir igharazim a givese, ez…® d…®penim…®n ghuavim ua uan d…®penim givezamin azenir vam…®ra iti.
\v 30 Eght…® azenir vam…®ra mang…®gh g…®vaght…®, a ua d…®penir kam givezeghan kogham, a dat…®r…®gh…®n uam ivezamin tuaviba puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®penir kam, a gumazir a givezamin d…®penim, ko an ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba, a g…®n men d…®penim…®n ikiam. Egh azenir biziba ua da ikarvaghamin dughiam…®n, a uam a dan…®ngan kogham.
\v 31 Eght…® nguibar dozir d…®vaziba puvat…®ziba, dar aven itir d…®peniba, ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, da mati nguazir dagheba oparim. Kamagh…®n, d…®penibar ghuaviba ua d…®penir kabagh ivezam. Eght…® azenir ua biziba ikarvaghamim…®n, gumazir dagh ivezeziba, ua da is…® guiz…®n d…®penir ghuavibar an…®ngam.
\v 32 Eght…® Livain anabam…®n adarazi arazir kam…®n g…®n mangan mark…®. Me, d…®vazim av…®nizir nguibar ekiam…®n itir d…®penim uam a gives…®, me a givesegh.
\v 33 Egh Livain anabam…®n tav uan d…®penim amadagh, egh uam a givezan aghuaght…®, gumazir d…®penir kam givezezim, azenir biziba ua da ikarvaghamim…®n, a ua d…®penim is…® Livain gumazir kam dan…®ngigh. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Israelian anabar igharaziba bagha nguazibagh inamigha me gan…®ngi. Ez…® Livain anabam puvat…®. K…® Israelian anabar igharazibar nguazibar tong…®n, nguibar ekiar maba isa Livaibagh an…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, d…®penir Livain nguibar ekiam…®n itiba, da dughiabar zurara Livain d…®penibara.
\v 34 Egha uaghan, nguazir Livain anabam…®n nguibar ekiabar m…®riam…®n borogh…®n itiba, gumazir igharaziba dagh ivezan mark…®. Kar Livaibar nguazibara.‚Äù
\s1 Onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibar akurvazir araziba
\p 
\v 35 \x - \xo 25:35 \xt God…®n Araziba 15:7-8\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan namakabar tav, onganarazibagh amir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®va, bizibagh ivezamin dag…®aba puvat…®ght…®, ia uari an akurvagh, mati ia ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itibagh ami mogh…®n, an akurvagh. Kamagh…®n, ian namakar kam ia ko ikiam.
\v 36-37 \x - \xo 25:36-37 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:25; God…®n Araziba 23:19-20\x*Egh a pura ia da dag…®aba inigh, egh ua dag…®ar iniziba ikarvaghs…®, ia ua dag…®atam dagh is…®n dar…®ghan mark…®. Eght…® a daghebagh ivezt…®, ia ua dag…®ataba daghebar ivezim gis…®n dar…®ghan mark…®. Ia Godram atiating, egh uan namakaba ateght…® me ian tong…®n ik…®.
\v 38 K…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®kemegha g…®fa. K…® ian God…®n ikiasa, egha kamagh…®n, k…® Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha ian akua azenan iza, Kenan…®n nguazim ia dan…®ngasava ami.‚Äù
\s1 Ingangarir gumazamizir k…®niba damuamin araziba
\p 
\v 39 \x - \xo 25:39-46 \xt Ua Me Ini 21:2-6; God…®n Araziba 15:12-18\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam onganarazibar amuva, ia ateght…® ia ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n a givezegh, egh paz…® a damut…® a ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ian apengan ik…® ingaran mark…®, mati ik…®zir igharazibar ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ia bagha ingari.
\v 40 A mati gumazir dag…®aba bagha ingarim…®n m…®n ia ko ik…®, egh ian ingangaribar amu mang…®t…® azenir ua biziba ikarvaghamim otogham.
\v 41 Egh azenir kam…®n a uan amuim ko boriba sara, me f…®righ…®regh ia ategh ua uan adarazi bagh mang…®, uan inazir afeziabar nguazim…®n ikiam.
\v 42 Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n. Fom…®ra ia Israelia, kantri Isip…®n ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar itima, k…® ia inigha azenan izez…® ia bar Isip ataki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia nan ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®n otifi. Kamagh…®n, ia uan namakabagh ivezeght…®, me dughiabar zurara ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ikian kogham. Bar mark…®.
\v 43 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan namakar ia ivezeziba, puv…®ra me ab…®n me damut…®, me bar os…®mt…®zir dafaba sara ingangarir ekiabar amuan mark…®. Ia nan atiating, k…® ian God, egh ia deraghv…®ram me damu.
\p 
\v 44 ‚ÄúEgh ia ingangarir gumazamizir k…®niba inis…®, ik…®zir igharazir ian borogh…®n itiba da me inigh.
\v 45 Egh ia uaghan ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n ikia boriba bateziba, ia ingangarir gumazamizir k…®niba, me da dagh ivezam. Ia deragh me givezeght…®, me guizbang…®ra ian ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n otifigh.
\v 46 Eght…® ia g…®n ar…®m…®ghireght…®, ian ovavir boriba ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nir kaba inight…®, me zurara ian ovavir boribar ingangaribar amu mang…®v…®ra ikiam. Me iananaba. Eght…® ian namakabara, ian ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otivight…®, ia paza me damu me gativan mark…®. Ia deraghv…®ra me damu.
\p 
\v 47 ‚ÄúEght…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itibar tav, dag…®aba bar iz…®vagham, eght…® ia Israelia, ian tav onganarazibagh amir gumazim…®n m…®n otogh…®va, a ik…®zir igharazim…®n gumazir kam ateght…® an a givezeght…®, an an ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ikiam, o gumazir kam…®n tav…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n m…®n otogham.
\v 48 Israelian gumazir kam kamagh…®n damigham, eght…® ia uam a givezeght…®, kamagh…®n deragham. An aveghbuatam,
\v 49 o an afeziar dozim, o namakatam o anabatam, uam a givezeght…® deragham. Eght…® a uab…® dag…®ataba inigh, uab…® uab…® givezegh, egh ingangarir kurar kam atakigh.
\v 50 Gumazir kam, ik…®zir igharazim…®n gumazir a givezezim ko deraghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh uaning k…®m…®va fogh suam, azenir ikiav…®ra itiba me da meng mang…® azenir ua biziba ikarvaghamim…®n tugham. Eght…® gumazir, ingangarir gumazir kam givezezim suam, gumazir azenir kabar ingarir dag…®abar ivezim…®n d…®bobonim manmak…®n. Eght…® gumazir kam uab…®, o an anabatam ivezir kamagh…®n garimra uam a givesegh.
\v 51 Eght…® azenir av…®riba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, gumazir kam dag…®ar bar ekiam…®n ua gumazir a givezezir kam dan…®ngigh.
\v 52 Eght…® azenir av…®riba ikian koght…®, azenir biziba ua da ikarvaghamim otoght…®, a dag…®ar muziarim is…® ua gumazir kam dan…®ngigh.
\v 53 Eght…® ik…®zir igharazim…®n gumazir kam kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazim g…®n…®ghn…®gh suam, a mati azenibar vaghvagha a ko ikia dag…®aba bagha ingarir gumazim, egh a puv a m…®k…®m…®va, aneb…®n paz…® a damuan mark…®. An an asughasugh n…®m…®ram a damu.
\v 54 Eght…® me arazir kabar g…®n mang…®, ua gumazir kam givezan kogham. Eght…® azenir biziba ua da ikarvaghamim otoght…®, gumazir a givezezim aneteght…®, a f…®righ…®r…®gh mang…®va uan amuim ko boriba sara deraghv…®ra ikiam.
\p 
\v 55 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, k…® Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha azenan ize. Kamagh…®n, ia Israelia, ia nan ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uan tav ateght…®, a dughiabar zurara ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n ikian mark…®.‚Äù
\c 26
\s1 God deraghv…®ra uan gumazamizir an akam…®n g…®n zuibar amuam
\r (God…®n Araziba 7:12-24; 28:1-14)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 26:1 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:4; Ofa Gami 19:4; God…®n Araziba 5:8; 16:21-22\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa temer oteviba inigh dar asebar nedazibar ghoran mark…®, ia guarir ak…®nitam inigh uan nguazim…®n anesaragham, o dag…®atam inigh d…®ghoriba a daright…® da ian asebar marvir guabar m…®n gant…®, ia marvir guar kabar ziaba fan mark…®, da gavgaviba pu. Puvat…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia nan ziamra f…®.
\v 2 K…® ia bagha m…®sevezir Sabat…®n dughiabar, ia ingaran mark…®. Ia puram avughs…®. Egh ia bar nan Purirpenim gifongegh a baghv…®ra ik…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®kemegha g…®fa.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 26:3-5 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:13-15; 28:1-14\x*‚ÄúEgh ia nan arazir k…® ifongezibar g…®n mang…®, nan Akar Gavgaviba baragh, egh dar amu,
\v 4 eght…® k…® amozim damut…®, a uan izir dughiamra izam. Eght…® k…® ian daghebar amut…®, da deraghv…®ra ian nguazim…®n otivt…®, temeba b…®va ov…®zir av…®riba ikiam.
\v 5 Ia dagher bar av…®riba ik…®va, egh wit…®n and…®ziba ini mang…®, ia wain…®n ov…®zir an…®diziba iniamim…®n dughiam…®n tugham. Egh ia wain…®n ov…®ziba ini mang…®, dughiar ia dagheba oparamim…®n tugham. Ia dam…®va naviba bar izevegham. Egh ia deraghv…®ra uan nguazim dapiagham.
\p 
\v 6 ‚ÄúEght…® k…® navir am…®rizim ia danight…® ia deraghv…®ra dapiagh, egh dakuamin dughiam…®n, ia bizitam…®n atiatingan kogham. K…® as…®zir atiar m…®soziba ian nguazim…®n da batueght…® apaniba nguazir kam…®n ia m…®soghan kogham.
\v 7 Eght…® ia apanibav sogh me ab…®nt…®, men av…®rim ian damazim…®n ar…®ghiram.
\v 8 Ian 5plan m…®dorozir gumaziba 100plan apaniba ab…®nigham. Eght…® ian 100plan m…®dorozir gumaziba 10,000plan apaniba ab…®nigham. Guizbang…®ra, ian apaniba bar ian damazim…®n ar…®ghiregham.
\v 9 Eght…® k…® deraghv…®ra ia damuva borir av…®riba ia dan…®ng, egh ia damut…®, ia bar av…®rasemegham. Eght…® Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir k…® fom…®ra ia ko amizir kam, k…® gavgavim a dan…®ngam.
\v 10 Eght…® azenir g…®vazim…®n dagheba, da ik…®v…®ra ik…® mang…® azenir igharazim batogham. Eght…® dagher naba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, ia dagher igiar and…®ziba iniva, ghuriba makunigh, egh dagher igiaba dar danganim dar…®gham.
\v 11 Eght…® k…® ian tong…®n ik…®v…®ra ik…®, ak…®rim ragh ia gasaraghan kogham.
\v 12 \x - \xo 26:12 \xt 2 Korin 6:16\x*K…® ian tong…®n daruva ian God…®n ikiam. Eght…® ia nan gumazamizibar ikiam.
\v 13 K…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian God. Ia fom…®ra Isip…®n kantrin aven ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar ikez…®, k…® ian os…®mt…®zim ag…®vagha ian akua azenan ize. K…® ia isa kalabus gat…®zir gumazibar gavgaviba ab…®ghiz…®, ia kalabus ategha bar akongegha ize.‚Äù
\s1 God gumazamizir an akam batoziba ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam
\r (God…®n Araziba 28:15-68)
\p 
\v 14 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nan akaba baraghan aghuagh, egh nan Akar Gavgavir kabar g…®n mangan koght…®, k…® ivezir kuram ia dan…®ngam.
\v 15 Ia ak…®rim ragh nan arazir k…® ifongezibagh asaragh, nan bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemezibar aghuagh…®va, nan Akar Gavgaviba baraghan kogh…®va, egh nan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir k…® ia ko amizir kam abight…®,
\v 16 kamagh…®n k…® bizitam…®n ia damuam. K…® zuam…®ra ia damight…®, ia bar ikuvigh bar atiatigham. K…® ia damut…®, ia ar…®mariar bar ekiaba iniva, ian m…®karziba puv fengt…®, ian damaziba okavight…®, ian m…®karziba n…®m…®ra su mag…®r…® mang…® bar ikuvigham. Ia azenibar dagheba opar, egh ia dar daghebar aman kogham. Apanibara, da ini dar amam.
\v 17 Egh k…® uab…® ian apanim damuam. K…® gumazir igharaziba amadaght…®, me iz…® ia m…®sogh ia d…®kab…®nam. Eght…® gumazir kaba ia gativagham. Apaniba t…®ghar ia bagh iz…® ia g…®nt…®ghamin dughiam…®n, ia puram atiating aregham.
\p 
