\v 21 ‚ÄúOs…®mt…®zir kaba ia bativt…®, ia oraghan koght…®, k…® ian arazir kurar kabagh n…®ghn…®gh, egh k…® os…®mt…®ziba ia dar…®ghv…®ra ikiam.
