\v 40 ‚ÄúEght…® g…®n ian ik…®v…®ra ikiamin varazira, me uan arazir kurabagh n…®ghn…®gh dar gun na m…®k…®mam. Egh me kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòE uan inazir afeziaba ko arazir kuram gami. E n…® barazir puvat…®gha n…®n akaba batoke.‚Äô
