\v 42 \x - \xo 26:42 \xt Jenesis 17:7-8; 26:3-4; 28:13-14\x*k…® ua uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim ko nguazir kam gin…®r…®gham. Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam, k…® Abraham, Aisak, Jekop ko a gamua ghaze, k…® nguazir kam is…® men ovavir boribar an…®ngam.
