\v 46 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bizir a damuasa Israelia m…®kemezir kaba, ko arazir a ifongeziba, ko an Arazir kaba, a Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n bar da isa Moses gan…®ngi. Egha ghaze, Israelia bar dar g…®n mang…®.
\c 27
\s1 Gumazamiziba God gan…®dir bizibar Arazir maba
\p 
\v 1-2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam uab…® is…® na dan…®ng…®s…®, o gumazamizir igharazitam is…® na dan…®ngasa akar d…®k…®r…®zim na koma a gami, a uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®s…®, a dag…®ataba is…® ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngigh.
\v 3 Gumazamiziba uarigh ivezamin dag…®ar d…®bobonim kamak…®n. Gumazir 20plan azenibar ikegh mang…® 60plan azenibar tughamim, me 500 kinan a givezam.
\v 4 Egh amizir 20plan azenibar ikegh mang…® 60plan azenibar tughamim, me 300 kinan a givezam.
\v 5 Egh otarir 5plan azenibar ikegh mang…® 20plan azenibar tughamim, me 200 kinan a givezam. Eght…® amizir 5plan azenibar ikegh mang…® 20plan azenibar tughamim, me 100 kinan a givezam.
\v 6 Egh otarir iak…®nir vam…®ran ikegh mang…® 5plan azenibar tughamim, me 50 kinan, a givezam. Eght…® borir guivir iak…®nir vam…®ran ikegh mang…® 5plan azenibar tughamim, me 30 kinan a givezam.
\v 7 Eght…® gumazir 60plan azenibagh afirazim, me 150 kinan a givezam. Eght…® amizir 60plan azenibagh afirazim, me 100 kinan a givezam.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamizim, a uab…® uab…® givezamin dag…®aba, o uan namakam givezamin dag…®aba puvat…®gh, gumazir kam ofa gamir gumazim bagh mang…®. Eght…® ofa gamir gumazim ivezir kam gis…®vagh mag…®r…® gumazir kam damuamin ababanim…®n tught…®, gumazir kam ivezam.
